{"type":"message","id":"4798c824","parentId":"2f02dd05","timestamp":"2026-04-10T02:21:01.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要密码。我无法在这里输入密码。让我告诉用户如何手动安装。","thinkingSignature":"84d0ff84b369841c2f346276955f4a7103b55b0a88c48914d4a56f7392e783ec"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n需要 sudo 权限，但在这个环境里我没法输入密码。你可以自己在终端运行：\n\n```bash\nsudo npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n或者，如果你不想用 sudo，也可以指定一个你有权限的目录来安装：\n\n```bash\nnpm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code --prefix ~/.local\n```\n\n装完之后运行 `claude` 就能启动 Claude Code 了。有什么问题再告诉我 🙂"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":140,"output":108,"cacheRead":21056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21304,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775787655276,"responseId":"062791879dcbc4b908f03cd8214df705"}}
