{"type":"message","id":"6804e86b","parentId":"79ee9f08","timestamp":"2026-04-10T02:22:13.494Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they want the Claude Code app (the desktop application/GUI), not the CLI tool. They're saying they can already run it in the terminal. Let me check if there's a Claude Code desktop app available.\n\nClaude Code is primarily a CLI tool, but there might be a desktop app or an MCP harness version. Let me search for what's available.\n\nActually, thinking about this more - Claude Code from Anthropic is indeed a CLI tool that runs in the terminal. I'm not aware of a separate \"desktop app\" for Claude Code. \n\nMaybe the user is confused, or maybe they're referring to something else like the Claude app (claude.ai) which has a web interface and possibly desktop/mobile apps.\n \nWait, there's also the MCP Claude Code harness that OpenClaw supports, which lets you run Claude Code within OpenClaw as a coding agent. Perhaps they're looking for the Claude consumer app with a desktop version. I should clarify what they're actually trying to access.","thinkingSignature":"fde51652bf2f4d71e76db36ff766639f417e89356dccc2a050e23e994ec79992"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nClaude Code 本身是终端/CLI 工具，没有独立的桌面 App。你现在能在终端运行 `claude` 就说明装好了。\n\n你具体想要的是什么？\n- **网页版** Claude (claude.ai) — 有 Web UI，在浏览器用\n- **Mac/iOS App** — Anthropic 的官方 Claude App（不是 Claude Code）\n- **还是想通过 OpenClaw** 来用 Claude Code？我可以直接帮你 spawn 一个\n\n告诉我你想怎么用，我帮你搞定 🙂"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":335,"output":300,"cacheRead":21184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21819,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775787721353,"responseId":"062791c93af300d0b15e57db628b4b9e"}}
