{"type":"message","id":"2b628e6d","parentId":"09b99058","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:07:57.751Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52b2d60ca4a4c441fafd70f2f3e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 11:07 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b52b2d60ca4a4c441fafd70f2f3e]\n张玲: 我现在还没实现系统自动交易，因为我还想验证目前使用的策略的有效性和收益情况。所以第一个单点故障风险我认为现在不用管。我电脑里已经安装饿了docker，但是主要用于备份聊天记录，你可以考虑给我增加量化系统的容器功能。其余的问题你做一个详细的优化方案，给我。"}],"timestamp":1775790477747}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e384a15","parentId":"2b628e6d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:12:03.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":" 明白，你目前处于策略验证阶段，还没有上实盘自动交易。那我针对你的实际情况，重新调整优先级，给你一个可落地的优化方案。\n\n---\n\n# 个人量化系统优化方案（策略验证阶段）\n\n## 当前阶段定位\n- **阶段**：策略研发 & 回测验证期\n- **目标**：建立规范化的策略验证流程，为实盘自动化做准备\n- **暂不处理**：自动交易、实时风控、高可用架构\n\n---\n\n## 一、Docker 量化容器化方案\n\n既然你已有 Docker 用于备份，我帮你扩展一个量化专用的容器环境。\n\n### 建议容器架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    Docker Host (你的Mac)                 │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────────┐ │\n│  │  quant-jupyter  │  │  quant-backtest │  │  quant-database │ │\n│  │  (研发环境)    │  │  (回测引擎)    │  │  (数据存储)    │ │\n│  │              │  │              │  │                │ │\n│  │  - Jupyter   │  │  - Backtrader │  │  - PostgreSQL  │ │\n│  │  - Python    │  │  - Zipline    │  │  - TimescaleDB │ │\n│  │  - NumPy/Pandas│ │  - 自定义框架  │  │  - 行情数据    │ │\n│  │  - TA-Lib    │  │  - 绩效分析    │  │  - 特征数据    │ │\n│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────────┘ │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Docker Compose 配置\n\n```yaml\n# ~/quant/docker-compose.yml\nversion: '3.8'\n\nservices:\n  # 1. Jupyter 研发环境\n  quant-jupyter:\n    image: jupyter/scipy-notebook:latest\n    container_name: quant-jupyter\n    ports:\n      - \"8888:8888\"\n    volumes:\n      - ./notebooks:/home/jovyan/notebooks\n      - ./strategies:/home/jovyan/strategies\n      - ./data:/home/jovyan/data\n    environment:\n      - JUPYTER_ENABLE_LAB=yes\n    command: start-notebook.sh --NotebookApp.token='' --NotebookApp.password=''\n    networks:\n      - quant-network\n\n  # 2. 回测引擎 (自定义Python环境)\n  quant-backtest:\n    build: ./backtest\n    container_name: quant-backtest\n    volumes:\n      - ./strategies:/app/strategies\n      - ./data:/app/data\n      - ./results:/app/results\n      - ./backtest/config:/app/config\n    environment:\n      - PYTHONPATH=/app\n    networks:\n      - quant-network\n\n  # 3. 时序数据库 (行情数据)\n  quant-db:\n    image: timescale/timescaledb:latest-pg15\n    container_name: quant-db\n    ports:\n      - \"5432:5432\"\n    volumes:\n      - postgres_data:/var/lib/postgresql/data\n      - ./init-scripts:/docker-entrypoint-initdb.d\n    environment:\n      - POSTGRES_USER=quant\n      - POSTGRES_PASSWORD=quant_pass\n      - POSTGRES_DB=quant_db\n    networks:\n      - quant-network\n\n  # 4. 数据同步服务 (AKShare/Tushare)\n  quant-data-sync:\n    build: ./data-sync\n    container_name: quant-data-sync\n    volumes:\n      - ./data:/app/data\n      - ./data-sync/config:/app/config\n    environment:\n      - DB_HOST=quant-db\n      - DB_PORT=5432\n      - DB_USER=quant\n      - DB_PASS=quant_pass\n    depends_on:\n      - quant-db\n    networks:\n      - quant-network\n\nvolumes:\n  postgres_data:\n\nnetworks:\n  quant-network:\n    driver: bridge\n```\n\n### 快速启动脚本\n\n```bash\n# ~/quant/start.sh\n#!/bin/bash\n\ncd \"$(dirname \"$0\")\"\n\necho \"🚀 启动量化环境...\"\n\n# 创建必要目录\nmkdir -p notebooks strategies data results logs\n\n# 启动服务\ndocker-compose up -d\n\necho \"✅ 服务已启动\"\necho \"\"\necho \"访问地址：\"\necho \"  📓 Jupyter: http://localhost:8888\"\necho \"  🗄️  数据库: localhost:5432\"\necho \"\"\necho \"查看日志: docker-compose logs -f\"\necho \"停止服务: docker-compose down\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 二、策略验证阶段核心优化方案\n\n### 1. 策略回测规范化（P0）\n\n#### 当前问题\n- 回测代码分散，每个策略写法不一\n- 缺乏统一的绩效评估标准\n- 未考虑交易成本、滑点\n\n#### 优化方案：统一回测框架\n\n```python\n# strategies/framework/backtest_engine.py\n\"\"\"\n统一回测框架 - 所有策略必须继承此类\n\"\"\"\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom typing import Dict, List, Optional, Callable\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport json\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass BacktestConfig:\n    \"\"\"回测配置\"\"\"\n    start_date: str\n    end_date: str\n    initial_capital: float = 1_000_000\n    commission_rate: float = 0.0003  # 万3佣金\n    slippage: float = 0.001  # 千1滑点\n    stamp_duty: float = 0.001  # 千1印花税(卖出)\n    position_limit: float = 0.95  # 最大仓位限制\n\n\n@dataclass  \nclass TradeRecord:\n    \"\"\"交易记录\"\"\"\n    date: datetime\n    symbol: str\n    action: str  # BUY/SELL\n    price: float\n    shares: int\n    commission: float\n    slippage: float\n\n\nclass BaseStrategy:\n    \"\"\"\n    策略基类 - 所有策略必须继承\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, config: BacktestConfig):\n        self.config = config\n        self.capital = config.initial_capital\n        self.positions: Dict[str, int] = {}  # 当前持仓\n        self.trades: List[TradeRecord] = []  # 交易记录\n        self.daily_values: List[Dict] = []   # 每日净值\n        \n    def initialize(self, data: pd.DataFrame):\n        \"\"\"策略初始化，加载数据\"\"\"\n        self.data = data\n        self.current_idx = 0\n        \n    def on_bar(self, date: datetime, bar_data: pd.Series) -> Optional[Dict]:\n        \"\"\"\n        每个Bar触发，返回交易信号\n        Returns: {'action': 'BUY'/'SELL', 'symbol': '000001.SZ', 'weight': 0.5}\n        \"\"\"\n        raise NotImplementedError(\"子类必须实现此方法\")\n        \n    def calculate_metrics(self) -> Dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        计算绩效指标 - 统一标准\n        \"\"\"\n        if not self.daily_values:\n            return {}\n            \n        df = pd.DataFrame(self.daily_values)\n        df.set_index('date', inplace=True)\n        \n        # 收益率序列\n        returns = df['total_value'].pct_change().dropna()\n        \n        # 核心指标\n        total_return = (df['total_value'].iloc[-1] / self.config.initial_capital - 1) * 100\n        annual_return = ((1 + total_return/100) ** (252 / len(df)) - 1) * 100\n        \n        # 风险指标\n        volatility = returns.std() * np.sqrt(252) * 100\n        max_drawdown = self._calc_max_drawdown(df['total_value']) * 100\n        \n        # 风险调整收益\n        sharpe = (annual_return - 3) / volatility if volatility > 0 else 0  # 假设无风险利率3%\n        sortino = self._calc_sortino(returns, annual_return)\n        calmar = annual_return / abs(max_drawdown) if max_drawdown != 0 else 0\n        \n        # 交易统计\n        win_rate = self._calc_win_rate()\n        profit_factor = self._calc_profit_factor()\n        \n        return {\n            'total_return': round(total_return, 2),\n            'annual_return': round(annual_return, 2),\n            'volatility': round(volatility, 2),\n            'max_drawdown': round(max_drawdown, 2),\n            'sharpe_ratio': round(sharpe, 3),\n            'sortino_ratio': round(sortino, 3),\n            'calmar_ratio': round(calmar, 3),\n            'win_rate': round(win_rate, 2),\n            'profit_factor': round(profit_factor, 2),\n            'total_trades': len(self.trades),\n            'avg_trade_return': round(total_return / max(len(self.trades), 1), 3),\n        }\n        \n    def _calc_max_drawdown(self, values: pd.Series) -> float:\n        \"\"\"计算最大回撤\"\"\"\n        cummax = values.cummax()\n        drawdown = (values - cummax) / cummax\n        return drawdown.min()\n        \n    def _calc_sortino(self, returns: pd.Series, annual_return: float) -> float:\n        \"\"\"计算索提诺比率\"\"\"\n        downside = returns[returns < 0].std() * np.sqrt(252)\n        return (annual_return - 3) / (downside * 100) if downside > 0 else 0\n        \n    def _calc_win_rate(self) -> float:\n        \"\"\"计算胜率\"\"\"\n        if not self.trades:\n            return 0\n        # 简化计算：根据持仓变化判断\n        return 50.0  # 占位\n        \n    def _calc_profit_factor(self) -> float:\n        \"\"\"计算盈亏比\"\"\"\n        return 1.5  # 占位\n        \n    def run_backtest(self, data: pd.DataFrame) -> Dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        运行回测\n        \"\"\"\n        self.initialize(data)\n        \n        for idx, (date, row) in enumerate(data.iterrows()):\n            self.current_idx = idx\n            \n            # 获取信号\n            signal = self.on_bar(date, row)\n            \n            # 执行交易\n            if signal:\n                self._execute_trade(date, signal)\n                \n            # 记录每日净值\n            self._record_daily_value(date)\n            \n        return self.calculate_metrics()\n        \n    def _execute_trade(self, date: datetime, signal: Dict):\n        \"\"\"执行交易（简化版）\"\"\"\n        # 实际实现需考虑仓位、资金等\n        pass\n        \n    def _record_daily_value(self, date: datetime):\n        \"\"\"记录每日净值\"\"\"\n        # 计算当前持仓市值\n        position_value = sum(\n            shares * self.data.loc[date, 'close'] \n            for symbol, shares in self.positions.items()\n        )\n        \n        self.daily_values.append({\n            'date': date,\n            'cash': self.capital,\n            'position_value': position_value,\n            'total_value': self.capital + position_value\n        })\n\n\nclass BacktestReporter:\n    \"\"\"\n    回测报告生成器\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    @staticmethod\n    def generate_report(strategy_name: str, metrics: Dict, output_path: str):\n        \"\"\"生成标准化回测报告\"\"\"\n        \n        report = f\"\"\"\n# 策略回测报告\n\n## 基本信息\n- 策略名称: {strategy_name}\n- 生成时间: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\n- 回测区间: {metrics.get('start_date', 'N/A')} ~ {metrics.get('end_date', 'N/A')}\n\n## 收益指标\n| 指标 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| 总收益率 | {metrics['total_return']}% |\n| 年化收益率 | {metrics['annual_return']}% |\n| 夏普比率 | {metrics['sharpe_ratio']} |\n| 索提诺比率 | {metrics['sortino_ratio']} |\n| 卡尔玛比率 | {metrics['calmar_ratio']} |\n\n## 风险指标\n| 指标 | 数值 |\n|------|------|\n| 年化波动率 | {metrics['volatility']}% |\n| 最大回撤 | {metrics['max_drawdown']}% |\n| 胜率 | {metrics['win_rate']}% |\n| 盈亏比 | {metrics['profit_factor']} |\n\n## 交易统计\n- 总交易次数: {metrics['total_trades']}\n- 平均单次收益: {metrics['avg_trade_return']}%\n\n## 综合评价\n{BacktestReporter._evaluate(metrics)}\n\"\"\"\n        \n        with open(output_path, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            f.write(report)\n            \n        return report\n        \n    @staticmethod\n    def _evaluate(metrics: Dict) -> str:\n        \"\"\"生成评价\"\"\"\n        score = 0\n        \n        if metrics['sharpe_ratio'] > 1.5:\n            score += 2\n        elif metrics['sharpe_ratio'] > 1:\n            score += 1\n            \n        if metrics['max_drawdown'] > -20:\n            score += 2\n        elif metrics['max_drawdown'] > -30:\n            score += 1\n            \n        if metrics['total_return'] > 50:\n            score += 1\n            \n        evaluations = {\n            5: \"🟢 优秀策略：风险收益比良好，建议小资金实盘测试\",\n            4: \"🟡 良好策略：具备实盘价值，建议优化后测试\",\n            3: \"🟡 一般策略：需进一步优化，暂不建议实盘\",\n            2: \"🔴 较差策略：风险过高或收益不足，需大幅改进\",\n            1: \"🔴 不合格策略：不建议使用\",\n            0: \"🔴 不合格策略：不建议使用\"\n        }\n        \n        return evaluations.get(score, \"需进一步分析\")\n```\n\n#### 使用示例\n\n```python\n# strategies/demo_strategy.py\nfrom framework.backtest_engine import BaseStrategy, BacktestConfig\nimport pandas as pd\n\n\nclass DemoStrategy(BaseStrategy):\n    \"\"\"\n    示例策略：双均线突破\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, config: BacktestConfig, short_window=5, long_window=20):\n        super().__init__(config)\n        self.short_window = short_window\n        self.long_window = long_window\n        \n    def on_bar(self, date, bar_data):\n        # 获取历史数据计算均线\n        if self.current_idx < self.long_window:\n            return None\n            \n        hist = self.data.iloc[self.current_idx-self.long_window:self.current_idx]\n        ma_short = hist['close'].tail(self.short_window).mean()\n        ma_long = hist['close'].mean()\n        \n        # 生成信号\n        if ma_short > ma_long and '000001.SZ' not in self.positions:\n            return {\n                'action': 'BUY',\n                'symbol': '000001.SZ',\n                'weight': 0.5\n            }\n        elif ma_short < ma_long and '000001.SZ' in self.positions:\n            return {\n                'action': 'SELL',\n                'symbol': '000001.SZ',\n                'weight': 0\n            }\n            \n        return None\n\n\n# 运行回测\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    # 加载数据\n    data = pd.read_csv('data/000001.SZ.csv', index_col='date', parse_dates=True)\n    \n    # 配置\n    config = BacktestConfig(\n        start_date='2020-01-01',\n        end_date='2023-12-31',\n        initial_capital=1_000_000,\n        commission_rate=0.0003,\n        slippage=0.001\n    )\n    \n    # 运行\n    strategy = DemoStrategy(config, short_window=5, long_window=20)\n    metrics = strategy.run_backtest(data)\n    \n    # 生成报告\n    from framework.backtest_engine import BacktestReporter\n    BacktestReporter.generate_report(\n        '双均线策略(5,20)', \n        metrics, \n        'results/demo_strategy_report.md'\n    )\n    \n    print(\"回测完成！\")\n    print(f\"总收益: {metrics['total_return']}%\")\n    print(f\"夏普比率: {metrics['sharpe_ratio']}\")\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. 数据质量保障（P1）\n\n#### 数据获取标准化\n\n```python\n# data-sync/data_fetcher.py\n\"\"\"\n统一数据获取模块\n\"\"\"\n\nimport akshare as ak\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom typing import Optional\nimport logging\n\nlogging.basicConfig(level=logging.INFO)\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n\nclass DataFetcher:\n    \"\"\"\n    数据获取统一接口\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self):\n        self.cache = {}\n        \n    def get_stock_daily(self, symbol: str, start_date: str, end_date: str) -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"\n        获取股票日线数据（带缓存）\n        \"\"\"\n        cache_key = f\"{symbol}_{start_date}_{end_date}\"\n        \n        if cache_key in self.cache:\n            logger.info(f\"使用缓存数据: {symbol}\")\n            return self.cache[cache_key]\n            \n        try:\n            # AKShare获取数据\n            df = ak.stock_zh_a_hist(\n                symbol=symbol.split('.')[0],  # 去掉后缀\n                period=\"daily\",\n                start_date=start_date.replace('-', ''),\n                end_date=end_date.replace('-', ''),\n                adjust=\"qfq\"  # 前复权\n            )\n            \n            # 标准化列名\n            df.columns = ['date', 'open', 'close', 'high', 'low', 'volume', \n                         'amount', 'amplitude', 'pct_change', 'change', 'turnover']\n            df['date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['date'])\n            df.set_index('date', inplace=True)\n            \n            # 数据质量检查\n            df = self._validate_data(df, symbol)\n            \n            self.cache[cache_key] = df\n            logger.info(f\"成功获取 {symbol}: {len(df)} 条记录\")\n            \n            return df\n            \n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.error(f\"获取数据失败 {symbol}: {e}\")\n            raise\n            \n    def _validate_data(self, df: pd.DataFrame, symbol: str) -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"\n        数据质量验证\n        \"\"\"\n        issues = []\n        \n        # 1. 检查缺失值\n        if df.isnull().any().any():\n            null_count = df.isnull().sum().sum()\n            issues.append(f\"存在 {null_count} 个缺失值\")\n            df = df.fillna(method='ffill').fillna(method='bfill')\n            \n        # 2. 检查价格异常\n        price_cols = ['open', 'high', 'low', 'close']\n        for col in price_cols:\n            if (df[col] <= 0).any():\n                issues.append(f\"{col} 存在非正价格\")\n                \n        # 3. 检查OHLC逻辑\n        invalid_ohlc = (\n            (df['high'] < df['low']) | \n            (df['high'] < df[['open', 'close']].max(axis=1)) |\n            (df['low'] > df[['open', 'close']].min(axis=1))\n        )\n        if invalid_ohlc.any():\n            issues.append(f\"{invalid_ohlc.sum()} 条记录 OHLC 逻辑异常\")\n            \n        # 4. 检查涨跌停价格异常（A股）\n        df['price_change'] = df['close'].pct_change()\n        limit_up = df['price_change'] > 0.21  # 考虑科创板、创业板\n        limit_down = df['price_change'] < -0.21\n        \n        if limit_up.any() or limit_down.any():\n            issues.append(f\"发现 {limit_up.sum()} 个涨停, {limit_down.sum()} 个跌停\")\n            \n        # 5. 检查成交量异常\n        zero_volume = (df['volume'] == 0).sum()\n        if zero_volume > 0:\n            issues.append(f\"{zero_volume} 条记录成交量为0\")\n            \n        if issues:\n            logger.warning(f\"[{symbol}] 数据质量问题: {'; '.join(issues)}\")\n        else:\n            logger.info(f\"[{symbol}] 数据质量检查通过\")\n            \n        return df\n        \n    def get_index_data(self, index_code: str = \"000001\") -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"\n        获取指数数据作为基准\n        \"\"\"\n        df = ak.index_zh_a_hist(\n            symbol=index_code,\n            period=\"daily\"\n        )\n        df.columns = ['date', 'open', 'close', 'high', 'low', 'volume', 'amount', 'amplitude']\n        df['date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['date'])\n        df.set_index('date', inplace=True)\n        return df\n\n\n# 数据更新脚本\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    fetcher = DataFetcher()\n    \n    # 获取沪深300成分股列表\n    stocks = ak.index_stock_cons_weight_csindex(symbol=\"000300\")\n    stock_list = stocks['成分券代码'].tolist()[:10]  # 先取前10只测试\n    \n    # 批量获取\n    for symbol in stock_list:\n        try:\n            df = fetcher.get_stock_daily(\n                symbol, \n                '2020-01-01', \n                datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')\n            )\n            # 保存到本地\n            df.to_csv(f'data/stocks/{symbol}.csv')\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.error(f\"处理 {symbol} 失败: {e}\")\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. 策略有效性验证（P1）\n\n#### 样本外测试框架\n\n```python\n# strategies/framework/validation.py\n\"\"\"\n策略验证框架 - 防止过拟合\n\"\"\"\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom typing import Dict, List, Tuple\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport json\n\n\nclass StrategyValidator:\n    \"\"\"\n    策略验证器 - 确保策略稳健性\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, data: pd.DataFrame):\n        self.data = data\n        \n    def walk_forward_analysis(self, strategy_class, config, \n                             train_size: int = 504,  # 约2年\n                             test_size: int = 63,    # 约3个月\n                             step_size: int = 63) -> Dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        滚动前向验证（Walk-Forward Analysis）\n        \n        这是防止过拟合的金标准\n        \"\"\"\n        results = []\n        n_samples = len(self.data)\n        \n        start_idx = 0\n        fold = 0\n        \n        while start_idx + train_size + test_size <= n_samples:\n            fold += 1\n            \n            # 划分训练集和测试集\n            train_start = start_idx\n            train_end = start_idx + train_size\n            test_end = train_end + test_size\n            \n            train_data = self.data.iloc[train_start:train_end]\n            test_data = self.data.iloc[train_end:test_end]\n            \n            # 在训练集上优化参数（简化版，实际可用网格搜索）\n            best_params = self._optimize_params(strategy_class, config, train_data)\n            \n            # 在测试集上验证\n            strategy = strategy_class(config, **best_params)\n            metrics = strategy.run_backtest(test_data)\n            \n            results.append({\n                'fold': fold,\n                'train_period': f\"{train_data.index[0]} ~ {train_data.index[-1]}\",\n                'test_period': f\"{test_data.index[0]} ~ {test_data.index[-1]}\",\n                'params': best_params,\n                'metrics': metrics\n            })\n            \n            print(f\"Fold {fold}: 训练期 {train_data.index[0].date()} ~ {train_data.index[-1].date()}, \"\n                  f\"测试期 {test_data.index[0].date()} ~ {test_data.index[-1].date()}, \"\n                  f\"收益 {metrics['total_return']:.2f}%, 夏普 {metrics['sharpe_ratio']:.3f}\")\n            \n            start_idx += step_size\n            \n        # 汇总结果\n        returns = [r['metrics']['total_return'] for r in results]\n        sharpes = [r['metrics']['sharpe_ratio'] for r in results]\n        \n        summary = {\n            'folds': results,\n            'avg_return': np.mean(returns),\n            'std_return': np.std(returns),\n            'min_return': np.min(returns),\n            'max_return': np.max(returns),\n            'avg_sharpe': np.mean(sharpes),\n            'sharpe_consistency': np.std(sharpes),  # 夏普比率稳定性\n            'positive_ratio': sum(1 for r in returns if r > 0) / len(returns),\n            'robust_score': self._calc_robust_score(results)\n        }\n        \n        return summary\n        \n    def _optimize_params(self, strategy_class, config, train_data) -> Dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        简化版参数优化 - 实际可用更复杂的方法\n        \"\"\"\n        # 示例：双均线策略的参数优化\n        best_sharpe = -np.inf\n        best_params = {}\n        \n        for short in [3, 5, 10]:\n            for long in [20, 30, 60]:\n                if short >= long:\n                    continue\n                    \n                strategy = strategy_class(config, short_window=short, long_window=long)\n                metrics = strategy.run_backtest(train_data)\n                \n                if metrics['sharpe_ratio'] > best_sharpe:\n                    best_sharpe = metrics['sharpe_ratio']\n                    best_params = {'short_window': short, 'long_window': long}\n                    \n        return best_params\n        \n    def _calc_robust_score(self, results: List[Dict]) -> float:\n        \"\"\"\n        计算稳健性评分 0-100\n        \"\"\"\n        returns = [r['metrics']['total_return'] for r in results]\n        sharpes = [r['metrics']['sharpe_ratio'] for r in results]\n        \n        score = 0\n        \n        # 1. 正收益比例 (30分)\n        positive_ratio = sum(1 for r in returns if r > 0) / len(returns)\n        score += positive_ratio * 30\n        \n        # 2. 收益稳定性 (30分)\n        if np.mean(returns) > 0:\n            consistency = max(0, 1 - np.std(returns) / abs(np.mean(returns)))\n            score += consistency * 30\n            \n        # 3. 夏普比率 (20分)\n        avg_sharpe = np.mean(sharpes)\n        score += min(avg_sharpe / 2, 1) * 20\n        \n        # 4. 最大回撤控制 (20分)\n        max_dd = max([r['metrics']['max_drawdown'] for r in results])\n        score += max(0, 1 - abs(max_dd) / 30) * 20\n        \n        return round(score, 2)\n        \n    def monte_carlo_simulation(self, returns: pd.Series, n_simulations: int = 1000) -> Dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        蒙特卡洛模拟 - 评估策略的随机性影响\n        \"\"\"\n        np.random.seed(42)\n        \n        simulated_cumrets = []\n        final_returns = []\n        max_drawdowns = []\n        \n        for _ in range(n_simulations):\n            # 随机打乱收益率顺序\n            shuffled = np.random.choice(returns, size=len(returns), replace=True)\n            cumret = (1 + shuffled).cumprod()\n            \n            simulated_cumrets.append(cumret)\n            final_returns.append(cumret[-1] - 1)\n            max_drawdowns.append(self._calc_max_drawdown_from_series(cumret))\n            \n        return {\n            'median_final_return': np.median(final_returns) * 100,\n            'percentile_5': np.percentile(final_returns, 5) * 100,\n            'percentile_95': np.percentile(final_returns, 95) * 100,\n            'prob_profit': sum(1 for r in final_returns if r > 0) / n_simulations * 100,\n            'median_max_dd': np.median(max_drawdowns) * 100,\n            'worst_case_dd': np.percentile(max_drawdowns, 95) * 100\n        }\n        \n    def _calc_max_drawdown_from_series(self, values: np.ndarray) -> float:\n        cummax = np.maximum.accumulate(values)\n        drawdown = (values - cummax) / cummax\n        return drawdown.min()\n\n\n# 使用示例\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    from demo_strategy import DemoStrategy, BacktestConfig\n    \n    # 加载数据\n    data = pd.read_csv('data/000001.SZ.csv', index_col='date', parse_dates=True)\n    \n    config = BacktestConfig(\n        initial_capital=1_000_000,\n        commission_rate=0.0003,\n        slippage=0.001\n    )\n    \n    # 滚动验证\n    validator = StrategyValidator(data)\n    wfa_result = validator.walk_forward_analysis(\n        DemoStrategy, \n        config,\n        train_size=504,\n        test_size=63,\n        step_size=63\n    )\n    \n    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*50)\n    print(\"滚动前向验证结果\")\n    print(\"=\"*50)\n    print(f\"平均收益: {wfa_result['avg_return']:.2f}%\")\n    print(f\"收益标准差: {wfa_result['std_return']:.2f}%\")\n    print(f\"正收益比例: {wfa_result['positive_ratio']*100:.1f}%\")\n    print(f\"平均夏普: {wfa_result['avg_sharpe']:.3f}\")\n    print(f\"稳健性评分: {wfa_result['robust_score']}/100\")\n    \n    if wfa_result['robust_score'] >= 70:\n        print(\"\\n✅ 策略通过稳健性测试，可考虑实盘\")\n    elif wfa_result['robust_score'] >= 50:\n        print(\"\\n⚠️  策略表现一般，建议优化\")\n    else:\n        print(\"\\n❌ 策略未通过测试，存在过拟合风险\")\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. 策略对比与选择（P2）\n\n```python\n# strategies/framework/strategy_comparison.py\n\"\"\"\n策略对比分析框架\n\"\"\"\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom typing import Dict, List\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n\n\nclass StrategyComparison:\n    \"\"\"\n    多策略对比分析\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self):\n        self.results = {}\n        \n    def add_strategy(self, name: str, daily_returns: pd.Series, \n                     trades: List[Dict] = None):\n        \"\"\"\n        添加策略结果\n        \"\"\"\n        self.results[name] = {\n            'returns': daily_returns,\n            'trades': trades or []\n        }\n        \n    def compare(self, benchmark: pd.Series = None) -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"\n        生成对比报告\n        \"\"\"\n        comparison = {}\n        \n        for name, data in self.results.items():\n            returns = data['returns']\n            \n            comparison[name] = {\n                '总收益': f\"{(returns.sum() * 100):.2f}%\",\n                '年化收益': f\"{(returns.mean() * 252 * 100):.2f}%\",\n                '年化波动': f\"{(returns.std() * np.sqrt(252) * 100):.2f}%\",\n                '夏普比率': f\"{(returns.mean() * 252 / (returns.std() * np.sqrt(252))):.3f}\",\n                '最大回撤': f\"{(self._calc_max_drawdown(returns) * 100):.2f}%\",\n                '胜率': f\"{(sum(returns > 0) / len(returns) * 100):.1f}%\",\n                '盈亏比': f\"{(abs(returns[returns > 0].mean() / returns[returns < 0].mean())):.2f}\",\n            }\n            \n        df = pd.DataFrame(comparison).T\n        \n        # 添加与基准的对比\n        if benchmark is not None:\n            df['超额收益'] = df['总收益'].apply(\n                lambda x: f\"{float(x.strip('%')) - (benchmark.sum() * 100):.2f}%\"\n            )\n            \n        return df\n        \n    def _calc_max_drawdown(self, returns: pd.Series) -> float:\n        cumret = (1 + returns).cumprod()\n        cummax = cumret.cummax()\n        drawdown = (cumret - cummax) / cummax\n        return drawdown.min()\n        \n    def plot_comparison(self, save_path: str = None):\n        \"\"\"\n        绘制对比图\n        \"\"\"\n        fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 2, figsize=(14, 10))\n        \n        # 1. 累计收益曲线\n        ax1 = axes[0, 0]\n        for name, data in self.results.items():\n            cumret = (1 + data['returns']).cumprod()\n            ax1.plot(cumret.index, cumret, label=name)\n        ax1.set_title('累计收益曲线')\n        ax1.legend()\n        ax1.set_ylabel('净值')\n        \n        # 2. 回撤曲线\n        ax2 = axes[0, 1]\n        for name, data in self.results.items():\n            cumret = (1 + data['returns']).cumprod()\n            cummax = cumret.cummax()\n            drawdown = (cumret - cummax) / cummax\n            ax2.fill_between(drawdown.index, drawdown, 0, alpha=0.3, label=name)\n        ax2.set_title('回撤曲线')\n        ax2.legend()\n        ax2.set_ylabel('回撤')\n        \n        # 3. 月度收益热力图\n        ax3 = axes[1, 0]\n        # 简化版，取第一个策略\n        first_strategy = list(self.results.keys())[0]\n        returns = self.results[first_strategy]['returns']\n        monthly = returns.resample('M').apply(lambda x: (1+x).prod() - 1)\n        monthly.index = monthly.index.to_period('M')\n        # 绘制柱状图\n        colors = ['green' if x > 0 else 'red' for x in monthly]\n        ax3.bar(range(len(monthly)), monthly * 100, color=colors)\n        ax3.set_title(f'{first_strategy} - 月度收益')\n        ax3.set_ylabel('收益 %')\n        \n        # 4. 收益分布\n        ax4 = axes[1, 1]\n        for name, data in self.results.items():\n            ax4.hist(data['returns'] * 100, bins=50, alpha=0.5, label=name)\n        ax4.set_title('日收益分布')\n        ax4.legend()\n        ax4.set_xlabel('收益 %')\n        \n        plt.tight_layout()\n        \n        if save_path:\n            plt.savefig(save_path, dpi=150, bbox_inches='tight')\n            \n        return fig\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、实施路线图\n\n### 第1周：环境搭建\n- [ ] 创建 Docker 量化容器配置\n- [ ] 搭建 Jupyter 研发环境\n- [ ] 配置 PostgreSQL + TimescaleDB 时序数据库\n- [ ] 实现数据获取自动化脚本\n\n### 第2周：框架开发\n- [ ] 完成统一回测框架（BaseStrategy）\n- [ ] 实现标准化绩效评估\n- [ ] 开发数据质量检查模块\n- [ ] 编写策略模板\n\n### 第3-4周：策略验证\n- [ ] 迁移现有策略到新框架\n- [ ] 进行滚动前向验证（Walk-Forward）\n- [ ] 蒙特卡洛稳健性测试\n- [ ] 生成对比报告，筛选有效策略\n\n### 第5-6周：监控体系\n- [ ] 搭建策略监控看板\n- [ ] 实现回测-模拟盘对比\n- [ ] 建立策略失效预警机制\n\n---\n\n需要我先把 Docker 配置文件和目录结构给你生成出来吗？或者你想先从哪个模块开始？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"camel-claude","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":26289,"output":7867,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34220,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775790477755,"responseId":"be003184d40d4f8e9a78349c968db576"}}
