{"type":"message","id":"c542235a","parentId":"20b5715a","timestamp":"2026-04-10T03:40:41.156Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":" 继续为你完善量化系统优化方案。接下来是**监控体系**和**实盘准备**部分。\n\n---\n\n## 四、策略监控与预警体系（P1）\n\n### 1. 策略健康度监控\n\n```python\n# monitoring/strategy_monitor.py\n\"\"\"\n策略监控中心 - 跟踪策略表现，及时发现问题\n\"\"\"\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom typing import Dict, List, Optional\nimport json\nimport logging\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass, asdict\n\nlogging.basicConfig(level=logging.INFO)\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass StrategyHealth:\n    \"\"\"策略健康度指标\"\"\"\n    strategy_name: str\n    date: datetime\n    status: str  # HEALTHY / WARNING / CRITICAL\n    \n    # 收益指标\n    total_return_7d: float\n    total_return_30d: float\n    total_return_90d: float\n    \n    # 风险指标\n    max_drawdown_current: float\n    volatility_30d: float\n    \n    # 质量指标\n    sharpe_30d: float\n    win_rate_30d: float\n    \n    # 异常标记\n    anomalies: List[str]\n    \n    def to_dict(self):\n        return asdict(self)\n\n\nclass StrategyMonitor:\n    \"\"\"\n    策略监控器\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    # 预警阈值配置\n    THRESHOLDS = {\n        'drawdown_warning': -0.10,      # 回撤10%警告\n        'drawdown_critical': -0.20,     # 回撤20%严重\n        'sharpe_min': 0.5,              # 夏普最低要求\n        'return_deviation': 0.20,       # 收益偏离预期20%\n        'consecutive_loss_days': 5,     # 连续亏损天数\n    }\n    \n    def __init__(self, history_file: str = 'monitoring/history.json'):\n        self.history_file = history_file\n        self.history = self._load_history()\n        \n    def _load_history(self) -> List[Dict]:\n        \"\"\"加载历史记录\"\"\"\n        try:\n            with open(self.history_file, 'r') as f:\n                return json.load(f)\n        except FileNotFoundError:\n            return []\n            \n    def _save_history(self):\n        \"\"\"保存历史记录\"\"\"\n        import os\n        os.makedirs(os.path.dirname(self.history_file), exist_ok=True)\n        with open(self.history_file, 'w') as f:\n            json.dump(self.history, f, indent=2, default=str)\n            \n    def check_strategy(self, strategy_name: str, \n                       daily_returns: pd.Series,\n                       expected_annual_return: float = 0.20) -> StrategyHealth:\n        \"\"\"\n        检查策略健康度\n        \"\"\"\n        anomalies = []\n        today = datetime.now()\n        \n        # 计算各周期收益\n        returns_7d = daily_returns.tail(7).sum() if len(daily_returns) >= 7 else 0\n        returns_30d = daily_returns.tail(30).sum() if len(daily_returns) >= 30 else 0\n        returns_90d = daily_returns.tail(90).sum() if len(daily_returns) >= 90 else 0\n        \n        # 计算当前回撤\n        cumret = (1 + daily_returns).cumprod()\n        running_max = cumret.expanding().max()\n        drawdown = (cumret - running_max) / running_max\n        current_dd = drawdown.iloc[-1]\n        \n        # 计算30天波动率和夏普\n        ret_30d = daily_returns.tail(30)\n        vol_30d = ret_30d.std() * np.sqrt(252) if len(ret_30d) > 0 else 0\n        sharpe_30d = (ret_30d.mean() * 252) / (ret_30d.std() * np.sqrt(252)) if ret_30d.std() > 0 else 0\n        \n        # 胜率\n        win_rate_30d = (ret_30d > 0).sum() / len(ret_30d) if len(ret_30d) > 0 else 0\n        \n        # 异常检测\n        # 1. 回撤检查\n        if current_dd < self.THRESHOLDS['drawdown_critical']:\n            anomalies.append(f\"严重回撤: {current_dd*100:.1f}%\")\n        elif current_dd < self.THRESHOLDS['drawdown_warning']:\n            anomalies.append(f\"回撤警告: {current_dd*100:.1f}%\")\n            \n        # 2. 夏普比率检查\n        if sharpe_30d < self.THRESHOLDS['sharpe_min'] and len(ret_30d) >= 30:\n            anomalies.append(f\"夏普过低: {sharpe_30d:.2f}\")\n            \n        # 3. 收益偏离检查（对比预期）\n        actual_annual = returns_30d * 12  # 简单年化\n        if abs(actual_annual - expected_annual_return) / expected_annual_return > self.THRESHOLDS['return_deviation']:\n            if actual_annual < expected_annual_return:\n                anomalies.append(f\"收益低于预期: 实际{actual_annual*100:.1f}% vs 预期{expected_annual_return*100:.1f}%\")\n                \n        # 4. 连续亏损检查\n        consecutive_losses = 0\n        for ret in reversed(daily_returns.tail(20)):\n            if ret < 0:\n                consecutive_losses += 1\n            else:\n                break\n        if consecutive_losses >= self.THRESHOLDS['consecutive_loss_days']:\n            anomalies.append(f\"连续亏损{consecutive_losses}天\")\n            \n        # 5. 波动率异常\n        hist_vol = daily_returns.std() * np.sqrt(252)\n        if vol_30d > hist_vol * 1.5:\n            anomalies.append(f\"波动率异常升高: {vol_30d*100:.1f}% vs 历史{hist_vol*100:.1f}%\")\n            \n        # 确定状态\n        if any(\"严重\" in a for a in anomalies):\n            status = \"CRITICAL\"\n        elif anomalies:\n            status = \"WARNING\"\n        else:\n            status = \"HEALTHY\"\n            \n        health = StrategyHealth(\n            strategy_name=strategy_name,\n            date=today,\n            status=status,\n            total_return_7d=round(returns_7d, 4),\n            total_return_30d=round(returns_30d, 4),\n            total_return_90d=round(returns_90d, 4),\n            max_drawdown_current=round(current_dd, 4),\n            volatility_30d=round(vol_30d, 4),\n            sharpe_30d=round(sharpe_30d, 3),\n            win_rate_30d=round(win_rate_30d, 3),\n            anomalies=anomalies\n        )\n        \n        # 保存记录\n        self.history.append(health.to_dict())\n        self._save_history()\n        \n        return health\n        \n    def generate_report(self, strategy_names: List[str] = None) -> str:\n        \"\"\"\n        生成监控报告\n        \"\"\"\n        if not self.history:\n            return \"暂无监控数据\"\n            \n        df = pd.DataFrame(self.history)\n        df['date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['date'])\n        \n        # 取最新记录\n        latest = df.sort_values('date').groupby('strategy_name').last()\n        \n        if strategy_names:\n            latest = latest.loc[latest.index.isin(strategy_names)]\n            \n        report = []\n        report.append(\"=\" * 60)\n        report.append(\"策略健康度监控报告\")\n        report.append(f\"生成时间: {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\")\n        report.append(\"=\" * 60)\n        \n        for name, row in latest.iterrows():\n            status_emoji = {\n                'HEALTHY': '🟢',\n                'WARNING': '🟡', \n                'CRITICAL': '🔴'\n            }.get(row['status'], '⚪')\n            \n            report.append(f\"\\n{status_emoji} {name} [{row['status']}]\")\n            report.append(f\"   7日收益: {row['total_return_7d']*100:.2f}%\")\n            report.append(f\"   30日收益: {row['total_return_30d']*100:.2f}%\")\n            report.append(f\"   当前回撤: {row['max_drawdown_current']*100:.2f}%\")\n            report.append(f\"   30日夏普: {row['sharpe_30d']:.2f}\")\n            \n            if row['anomalies']:\n                report.append(f\"   ⚠️ 异常: {'; '.join(row['anomalies'])}\")\n                \n        return '\\n'.join(report)\n        \n    def get_alerts(self) -> List[Dict]:\n        \"\"\"获取需要告警的策略\"\"\"\n        if not self.history:\n            return []\n            \n        latest = {}\n        for record in reversed(self.history):\n            name = record['strategy_name']\n            if name not in latest:\n                latest[name] = record\n                \n        alerts = []\n        for name, record in latest.items():\n            if record['status'] in ['WARNING', 'CRITICAL']:\n                alerts.append({\n                    'strategy': name,\n                    'status': record['status'],\n                    'anomalies': record['anomalies'],\n                    'time': record['date']\n                })\n                \n        return alerts\n\n\n# 定时监控脚本\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    import sys\n    \n    monitor = StrategyMonitor()\n    \n    # 示例：检查策略\n    # 实际使用时从数据库或文件加载策略收益数据\n    sample_returns = pd.Series(\n        np.random.normal(0.001, 0.02, 100),\n        index=pd.date_range(end=datetime.now(), periods=100, freq='D')\n    )\n    \n    health = monitor.check_strategy(\"双均线策略\", sample_returns)\n    \n    print(f\"\\n策略: {health.strategy_name}\")\n    print(f\"状态: {health.status}\")\n    print(f\"30日收益: {health.total_return_30d*100:.2f}%\")\n    print(f\"当前回撤: {health.max_drawdown_current*100:.2f}%\")\n    \n    if health.anomalies:\n        print(f\"\\n⚠️ 发现 {len(health.anomalies)} 个异常:\")\n        for a in health.anomalies:\n            print(f\"   - {a}\")\n            \n    # 生成完整报告\n    print(\"\\n\" + monitor.generate_report())\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. 回测 vs 实盘对比监控\n\n```python\n# monitoring/backtest_vs_live.py\n\"\"\"\n回测与实盘对比分析 - 检测策略失效\n\"\"\"\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom typing import Dict, Tuple\nimport scipy.stats as stats\n\n\nclass BacktestLiveComparator:\n    \"\"\"\n    回测与实盘对比分析器\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self):\n        self.divergence_threshold = 0.20  # 偏差20%触发警告\n        \n    def compare(self, \n                backtest_returns: pd.Series,\n                live_returns: pd.Series,\n                strategy_name: str = \"策略\") -> Dict:\n        \"\"\"\n        对比回测与实盘表现\n        \"\"\"\n        # 对齐时间\n        common_start = max(backtest_returns.index[0], live_returns.index[0])\n        common_end = min(backtest_returns.index[-1], live_returns.index[-1])\n        \n        bt = backtest_returns[common_start:common_end]\n        live = live_returns[common_start:common_end]\n        \n        if len(bt) != len(live):\n            # 重采样到相同频率\n            bt = bt.resample('D').sum().fillna(0)\n            live = live.resample('D').sum().fillna(0)\n            \n        # 计算累计收益\n        bt_cum = (1 + bt).cumprod()\n        live_cum = (1 + live).cumprod()\n        \n        # 各项指标对比\n        comparison = {\n            'strategy_name': strategy_name,\n            'period': f\"{common_start.date()} ~ {common_end.date()}\",\n            'days': len(bt),\n            \n            # 收益对比\n            'backtest_return': bt_cum.iloc[-1] - 1,\n            'live_return': live_cum.iloc[-1] - 1,\n            'return_gap': (live_cum.iloc[-1] - 1) - (bt_cum.iloc[-1] - 1),\n            'return_gap_pct': ((live_cum.iloc[-1] - 1) - (bt_cum.iloc[-1] - 1)) / abs(bt_cum.iloc[-1] - 1) if (bt_cum.iloc[-1] - 1) != 0 else 0,\n            \n            # 风险对比\n            'backtest_volatility': bt.std() * np.sqrt(252),\n            'live_volatility': live.std() * np.sqrt(252),\n            \n            # 夏普对比\n            'backtest_sharpe': bt.mean() * 252 / (bt.std() * np.sqrt(252)) if bt.std() > 0 else 0,\n            'live_sharpe': live.mean() * 252 / (live.std() * np.sqrt(252)) if live.std() > 0 else 0,\n            \n            # 统计检验\n            'mean_difference_tstat': self._t_test(bt, live),\n            'variance_ratio': (live.std() / bt.std()) ** 2 if bt.std() > 0 else 0,\n            \n            # 相关性\n            'correlation': bt.corr(live),\n        }\n        \n        # 评估偏差程度\n        comparison['divergence_level'] = self._assess_divergence(comparison)\n        \n        return comparison\n        \n    def _t_test(self, backtest: pd.Series, live: pd.Series) -> float:\n        \"\"\"t检验：均值差异显著性\"\"\"\n        try:\n            t_stat, p_value = stats.ttest_ind(backtest, live)\n            return {\n                't_statistic': float(t_stat),\n                'p_value': float(p_value),\n                'significant': p_value < 0.05\n            }\n        except:\n            return {'t_statistic': 0, 'p_value': 1, 'significant': False}\n            \n    def _assess_divergence(self, comparison: Dict) -> str:\n        \"\"\"评估偏差程度\"\"\"\n        gap_pct = abs(comparison['return_gap_pct'])\n        corr = comparison['correlation']\n        \n        if gap_pct > 0.5 or corr < 0.3:\n            return \"SEVERE\"  # 严重偏差\n        elif gap_pct > 0.2 or corr < 0.7:\n            return \"MODERATE\"  # 中度偏差\n        elif gap_pct > 0.1:\n            return \"MILD\"  # 轻度偏差\n        else:\n            return \"NORMAL\"  # 正常\n            \n    def generate_report(self, comparison: Dict) -> str:\n        \"\"\"生成对比报告\"\"\"\n        level_emoji = {\n            'NORMAL': '🟢',\n            'MILD': '🟡',\n            'MODERATE': '🟠',\n            'SEVERE': '🔴'\n        }\n        \n        emoji = level_emoji.get(comparison['divergence_level'], '⚪')\n        \n        report = f\"\"\"\n{emoji} 回测-实盘对比报告: {comparison['strategy_name']}\n{'='*60}\n\n对比期间: {comparison['period']} ({comparison['days']} 个交易日)\n\n【收益对比】\n  回测收益: {comparison['backtest_return']*100:.2f}%\n  实盘收益: {comparison['live_return']*100:.2f}%\n  收益差距: {comparison['return_gap']*100:.2f}% ({comparison['return_gap_pct']*100:+.1f}%)\n  \n【风险对比】\n  回测波动: {comparison['backtest_volatility']*100:.2f}%\n  实盘波动: {comparison['live_volatility']*100:.2f}%\n  方差比: {comparison['variance_ratio']:.2f}\n  \n【夏普对比】\n  回测夏普: {comparison['backtest_sharpe']:.3f}\n  实盘夏普: {comparison['live_sharpe']:.3f}\n  \n【相关性分析】\n  日收益相关系数: {comparison['correlation']:.3f}\n  \n【统计检验】\n  均值差异显著性: {'显著' if comparison['mean_difference_tstat']['significant'] else '不显著'}\n  (p-value: {comparison['mean_difference_tstat']['p_value']:.4f})\n\n【偏差评估】\n  偏差等级: {comparison['divergence_level']}\n  \n{self._get_recommendation(comparison['divergence_level'])}\n\"\"\"\n        return report\n        \n    def _get_recommendation(self, level: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"根据偏差等级给出建议\"\"\"\n        recommendations = {\n            'NORMAL': \"✅ 回测与实盘表现一致，策略可信度高\",\n            'MILD': \"⚠️ 存在轻微偏差，建议关注并分析原因（如滑点、交易成本）\",\n            'MODERATE': \"⚠️ 中度偏差！建议：\\n  1. 检查策略逻辑是否有未来函数\\n  2. 重新审视交易成本假设\\n  3. 考虑降低仓位或暂停策略\",\n            'SEVERE': \"🚨 严重偏差！策略可能失效，建议：\\n  1. 立即停止实盘交易\\n  2. 全面复盘策略逻辑\\n  3. 检查数据质量和执行问题\"\n        }\n        return recommendations.get(level, \"请人工评估\")\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、实盘准备清单\n\n当你准备从模拟盘进入实盘时，按以下清单逐一检查：\n\n### 阶段一：模拟盘验证（至少1个月）\n\n```markdown\n## 模拟盘验证清单\n\n### 信号生成\n- [ ] 每日信号自动生成，无人工干预\n- [ ] 信号与回测逻辑完全一致\n- [ ] 信号时间戳准确，无未来数据\n\n### 数据流\n- [ ] 实时数据延迟 < 1秒\n- [ ] 数据质量自动检查通过\n- [ ] 历史数据与实时数据格式一致\n\n### 监控\n- [ ] 每日自动生成交易报告\n- [ ] 策略健康度监控正常运行\n- [ ] 异常情况能及时发现并告警\n\n### 记录\n- [ ] 所有信号、委托、成交完整记录\n- [ ] 可追溯到每一笔交易的决策依据\n- [ ] 每日记录交易日志和心得\n```\n\n### 阶段二：小资金实盘（1-3个月）\n\n```markdown\n## 小资金实盘清单\n\n### 交易执行\n- [ ] 接入券商API，支持程序化下单\n- [ ] 下单前风控检查（仓位、金额限制）\n- [ ] 异常订单自动拦截\n- [ ] 支持手动紧急平仓\n\n### 风险控制（硬风控）\n- [ ] 单日最大亏损限额（如2%）\n- [ ] 单票最大仓位限制（如20%）\n- [ ] 总仓位上限（如80%）\n- [ ] 交易时间限制（如避开开盘前5分钟）\n\n### 监控告警\n- [ ] 实时盈亏监控\n- [ ] 回撤超限告警\n- [ ] 系统故障告警\n- [ ] 每日收盘后自动生成报告\n\n### 资金规模\n- [ ] 初始资金 < 总资产的10%\n- [ ] 单策略资金 < 初始资金的50%\n- [ ] 盈利20%后才考虑加仓\n```\n\n### 阶段三：逐步放大（3-6个月）\n\n```markdown\n## 规模放大清单\n\n### 业绩验证\n- [ ] 小资金实盘夏普 > 1.0\n- [ ] 最大回撤 < 15%\n- [ ] 连续3个月盈利\n- [ ] 回测-实盘偏差 < 20%\n\n### 系统稳定性\n- [ ] 连续运行3个月无重大故障\n- [ ] 故障恢复时间 < 30分钟\n- [ ] 数据完整性100%\n\n### 规模控制\n- [ ] 逐步加仓，每次增加不超过50%\n- [ ] 单策略容量测试通过\n- [ ] 冲击成本可控（滑点 < 0.1%）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、文件目录结构\n\n建议的完整目录结构：\n\n```\n~/quant/\n├── docker-compose.yml          # Docker编排\n├── start.sh                    # 一键启动脚本\n├── stop.sh                     # 停止脚本\n│\n├── notebooks/                  # Jupyter笔记本\n│   ├── research/              # 策略研究\n│   ├── analysis/              # 数据分析\n│   └── reports/               # 报告生成\n│\n├── strategies/                # 策略代码\n│   ├── framework/             # 回测框架\n│   │   ├── backtest_engine.py\n│   │   ├── validation.py\n│   │   ├── strategy_comparison.py\n│   │   └── utils.py\n│   ├── demo_strategy.py       # 示例策略\n│   └── your_strategies/       # 你的策略\n│\n├── data/                      # 数据目录\n│   ├── stocks/               # 股票数据\n│   ├── index/                # 指数数据\n│   ├── factors/              # 因子数据\n│   └── cache/                # 缓存数据\n│\n├── results/                   # 回测结果\n│   ├── backtest_reports/     # 回测报告\n│   ├── comparisons/          # 策略对比\n│   └── live_tracking/        # 实盘跟踪\n│\n├── monitoring/               # 监控模块\n│   ├── strategy_monitor.py\n│   ├── backtest_vs_live.py\n│   ├── alerts.py\n│   └── dashboard/            # 监控面板\n│\n├── config/                   # 配置文件\n│   ├── database.yml\n│   ├── strategy_config.yml\n│   └── risk_limits.yml\n│\n├── logs/                     # 日志文件\n└── docs/                     # 文档\n    ├── strategy_whitepapers/ # 策略白皮书\n    ├── meeting_notes/        # 会议纪要\n    └── lessons_learned.md    # 经验教训\n```\n\n---\n\n## 七、下一步行动\n\n你现在需要我帮你：\n\n1. **生成完整的 Docker 配置文件** - 可以直接运行的\n2. **编写策略模板** - 把你的现有策略迁移到新框架\n3. **搭建监控面板** - 用 Streamlit 或 Gradio 做可视化\n4. **数据自动同步脚本** - 定时从 AKShare 拉取数据\n\n你想先从哪个开始？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"camel-claude","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":37325,"output":4918,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42307,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775792262722,"responseId":"3f4a239a7dca4784af181b5f0eb41c50"}}
