{"type":"message","id":"ee568cba","parentId":"c1f5bbd0","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:26:01.958Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"         最后创建一个文档说明和快速启动指南："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.write:37","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 量化系统快速启动指南\n\n## 🚀 第一步：启动 Docker 环境\n\n```bash\ncd ~/quant\n./start.sh\n```\n\n等待所有服务启动完成，你会看到：\n- Jupyter Lab: http://localhost:8888 (Token: quant2024)\n- 监控面板: http://localhost:8501\n- PostgreSQL: localhost:5432\n\n## 📊 第二步：验证数据同步\n\n数据同步服务会自动运行，首次启动会同步沪深300成分股数据。\n\n检查数据是否同步成功：\n\n```bash\n# 进入数据库容器\ndocker-compose exec quant-db psql -U quant -d quant_db\n\n# 查询数据\nSELECT COUNT(*) FROM stock_daily;\nSELECT * FROM stock_daily LIMIT 5;\n```\n\n## 📝 第三步：开始策略研究\n\n### 方式1：使用 Jupyter Notebook\n\n1. 打开 http://localhost:8888\n2. 进入 `notebooks/research/`\n3. 打开 `00_quick_start.ipynb`\n4. 按步骤运行代码\n\n### 方式2：使用策略模板\n\n1. 复制模板文件：\n   ```bash\n   cp strategies/your_strategies/strategy_template.py strategies/your_strategies/my_strategy.py\n   ```\n\n2. 编辑 `my_strategy.py`，在 `on_bar` 方法中编写你的策略逻辑\n\n3. 运行回测：\n   ```bash\n   docker-compose exec quant-jupyter python /home/jovyan/strategies/your_strategies/my_strategy.py\n   ```\n\n## 🧪 第四步：策略验证\n\n在 Jupyter 中运行：\n\n```python\nfrom strategies.framework.validation import StrategyValidator\n\nvalidator = StrategyValidator(data)\nwfa_result = validator.walk_forward_analysis(\n    MyStrategy, \n    config,\n    train_size=504,\n    test_size=63,\n    step_size=63\n)\n\nprint(f\"稳健性评分: {wfa_result['robust_score']}/100\")\n```\n\n## 📈 第五步：监控策略表现\n\n1. 打开监控面板 http://localhost:8501\n2. 查看策略健康度\n3. 对比回测与实盘表现\n\n## 🛠️ 常用命令\n\n```bash\n# 查看服务状态\ndocker-compose ps\n\n# 查看日志\ndocker-compose logs -f quant-jupyter\ndocker-compose logs -f quant-data-sync\n\n# 进入 Jupyter 容器\ndocker-compose exec quant-jupyter bash\n\n# 重启服务\ndocker-compose restart quant-data-sync\n\n# 停止所有服务\n./stop.sh\n```\n\n## 📁 文件目录说明\n\n```\nquant/\n├── strategies/\n│   ├── framework/          # 回测框架（不要修改）\n│   │   ├── backtest_engine.py\n│   │   ├── validation.py\n│   │   └── strategy_comparison.py\n│   ├── demo_strategy.py    # 示例策略\n│   └── your_strategies/    # 你的策略放这里\n│       └── strategy_template.py\n│\n├── notebooks/\n│   └── research/\n│       └── 00_quick_start.ipynb\n│\n├── data/                   # 数据目录\n├── results/                # 回测结果\n└── monitoring/             # 监控模块\n```\n\n## ⚠️ 注意事项\n\n1. **首次启动**会下载 Docker 镜像，需要5-10分钟\n2. **数据同步**首次会同步大量数据，请耐心等待\n3. **内存要求**建议 Docker 分配至少 4GB 内存\n4. **备份**重要策略和数据请定期备份\n\n## 🆘 故障排查\n\n### 服务启动失败\n\n```bash\n# 检查 Docker 状态\ndocker info\n\n# 清理并重建\ndocker-compose down -v\ndocker-compose up --build\n```\n\n### 数据库连接失败\n\n```bash\n# 等待数据库完全启动\ndocker-compose logs -f quant-db\n\n# 手动初始化数据库\ndocker-compose exec quant-data-sync python /app/init_db.py\n```\n\n### 数据同步失败\n\n```bash\n# 检查网络连接\ndocker-compose exec quant-data-sync curl -I https://www.akshare.xyz\n\n# 手动运行同步\ndocker-compose exec quant-data-sync python /app/data_sync.py\n```\n\n## 📚 下一步\n\n- 阅读 `strategies/demo_strategy.py` 学习策略编写\n- 查看 `monitoring/strategy_monitor.py` 了解监控机制\n- 参考 `README.md` 获取更多详细信息\n\n祝你量化研究顺利！🎯\n","path":"/Users/ling/quant/QUICKSTART.md"}},{"type":"text","text":"  "}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"camel-claude","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":2229,"output":1089,"cacheRead":77568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80886,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775802319733,"responseId":"db1900e093874d039f2e863f1c2b4b0c"}}
