{"type":"message","id":"d49f78f1","parentId":"f4328c10","timestamp":"2026-04-10T06:27:41.329Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"               Docker 量化系统已全部创建完成！\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 完成清单\n\n### 核心组件\n\n| 模块 | 文件 | 功能 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Docker 编排** | `docker-compose.yml` | 6个服务：Jupyter、数据库、数据同步、监控面板、Redis、调度器 |\n| **回测框架** | `strategies/framework/` | 核心引擎 + 验证 + 对比分析 |\n| **监控模块** | `monitoring/` | 健康度监控 + 回测实盘对比 |\n| **数据同步** | `docker/data-sync/` | AKShare 自动同步 + TimescaleDB 存储 |\n| **策略模板** | `strategy_template.py` | 可直接复制使用 |\n| **监控面板** | Streamlit | 可视化监控界面 |\n\n### 访问地址\n\n```\n📓 Jupyter Lab    http://localhost:8888  (Token: quant2024)\n📊 监控面板       http://localhost:8501\n🗄️  PostgreSQL   localhost:5432         (quant/quant_pass)\n🔄 Redis          localhost:6379\n```\n\n### 启动命令\n\n```bash\ncd ~/quant\n./start.sh\n```\n\n### 文档\n\n- `QUICKSTART.md` - 快速入门\n- `README.md` - 详细说明\n- `FILE_MANIFEST.md` - 文件清单\n\n---\n\n系统已准备好，运行 `./start.sh` 即可启动！需要我解释任何部分或添加其他功能吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"camel-claude","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1304,"output":321,"cacheRead":81216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82841,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775802426881,"responseId":"2c7895d105554f8a8ec895e3bc30a83a"}}
