{"type":"message","id":"155faad2","parentId":"c7d8d83c","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:29:46.924Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_ND0oc3QTW45GG4PlrrNiKa","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Shrink Volume Pullback Strategy / 缩量回踩\n# Volume shrinks during pullback to MA5/MA10, then price bounces.\n\nname: shrink_pullback\ndisplay_name: 缩量回踩\ndescription: 检测缩量回踩均线支撑信号，趋势延续的理想入场点。\ncategory: trend\ncore_rules: [1, 2, 4]\nrequired_tools:\n  - get_daily_history\n  - analyze_trend\n  - get_realtime_quote\naliases: [缩量回踩, 回踩]\ndefault_router: true\ndefault_priority: 40\nmarket_regimes: [trending_down, sideways]\n\ninstructions: |\n  **缩量回踩（Shrink Volume Pullback Strategy）**\n\n  入场判定标准：\n\n  1. **前提条件**（关联理念2：趋势交易）：\n     - 股票必须处于上升趋势（MA5 > MA10 > MA20）。\n     - 使用 `analyze_trend` 确认多头排列。\n\n  2. **回踩检测**（关联理念4：买点偏好）：\n     - 使用 `get_daily_history` 和 `get_realtime_quote`。\n     - 价格回踩至 MA5 附近（误差 1% 以内）或 MA10 附近（误差 2% 以内）。\n     - 回调期间成交量 < 5 日均量的 70%（缩量特征）。\n     - `analyze_trend` → volume_status 应显示缩量。\n\n  3. **反弹信号**（关联理念1：严进策略）：\n     - 当前价格守住均线支撑位。\n     - MA5 乖离率 < 2% — 最佳买入区间。\n\n  4. **确认条件**（关联理念5：风险排查）：\n     - `search_stock_news` 无利空消息。\n     - 筹码分布健康（获利比例 50-80%）。\n\n  评分调整：\n  - 缩量回踩 MA5：sentiment_score +10\n  - 缩量回踩 MA10 且量能 < 0.6 倍均量：sentiment_score +8\n  - 理想买点设在 MA5 水平，次优买点设在 MA10。\n  - 止损设在 MA20 水平。\n  - 在 `buy_reason` 中注明\"缩量回踩\"。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775806186917}}
{"type":"message","id":"d83a6108","parentId":"155faad2","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:31:04.796Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我已经了解了你现有的策略库。这些是 YAML 描述性策略，主要用于信号分析。我来把它们迁移到可回测的 Python 框架里，同时开始回测验证。Docker 在后台继续构建。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_TxlDkkJWbQNNVBezYRysgj","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\n从 daily_stock_analysis 项目迁移的策略集\n\n基于原有 YAML 策略描述，转化为可回测的 Python 策略\n\"\"\"\n\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nfrom strategies.framework.backtest_engine import BaseStrategy, BacktestConfig\nfrom typing import Optional, Dict\n\n\nclass MAGoldenCrossStrategy(BaseStrategy):\n    \"\"\"\n    均线金叉策略\n    \n    来源: daily_stock_analysis/strategies/ma_golden_cross.yaml\n    \n    逻辑:\n    - 买入: MA5 上穿 MA10（金叉）+ 成交量 > 5日均量\n    - 卖出: MA5 下穿 MA10（死叉）\n    - 加强: MACD 金叉确认\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, config: BacktestConfig,\n                 ma_short: int = 5,\n                 ma_mid: int = 10,\n                 ma_long: int = 20,\n                 volume_ratio_min: float = 1.2,\n                 max_deviation: float = 0.05,\n                 position_pct: float = 0.8):\n        super().__init__(config)\n        self.ma_short = ma_short\n        self.ma_mid = ma_mid\n        self.ma_long = ma_long\n        self.volume_ratio_min = volume_ratio_min\n        self.max_deviation = max_deviation\n        self.position_pct = position_pct\n        \n    def on_bar(self, date, bar_data):\n        if self.current_idx < self.ma_long + 5:\n            return None\n            \n        hist = self.data.iloc[:self.current_idx + 1]\n        symbol = 'stock'\n        \n        # 计算均线\n        ma5 = hist['close'].rolling(self.ma_short).mean()\n        ma10 = hist['close'].rolling(self.ma_mid).mean()\n        ma20 = hist['close'].rolling(self.ma_long).mean()\n        \n        # 当前和前一根均线\n        curr_ma5, prev_ma5 = ma5.iloc[-1], ma5.iloc[-2]\n        curr_ma10, prev_ma10 = ma10.iloc[-1], ma10.iloc[-2]\n        \n        # 成交量\n        vol_avg5 = hist['volume'].rolling(5).mean().iloc[-1]\n        curr_vol = hist['volume'].iloc[-1]\n        volume_ratio = curr_vol / vol_avg5 if vol_avg5 > 0 else 0\n        \n        # 乖离率\n        deviation = (bar_data['close'] - curr_ma5) / curr_ma5 if curr_ma5 > 0 else 0\n        \n        current_position = self.positions.get(symbol, 0)\n        \n        # 买入信号: 金叉 + 量能确认 + 乖离率不过大\n        if (prev_ma5 <= prev_ma10 and curr_ma5 > curr_ma10 and\n            volume_ratio >= self.volume_ratio_min and\n            deviation < self.max_deviation):\n            \n            if current_position == 0:\n                target_value = self.capital * self.position_pct\n                shares = int(target_value / bar_data['close'] / 100) * 100\n                if shares > 0:\n                    return {'action': 'BUY', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': shares}\n                    \n        # 卖出信号: 死叉\n        elif prev_ma5 >= prev_ma10 and curr_ma5 < curr_ma10:\n            if current_position > 0:\n                return {'action': 'SELL', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': current_position}\n                \n        return None\n\n\nclass VolumeBreakoutStrategy(BaseStrategy):\n    \"\"\"\n    放量突���策略\n    \n    来源: daily_stock_analysis/strategies/volume_breakout.yaml\n    \n    逻辑:\n    - 买入: 价格突破20日高点 + 成交量 > 5日均量2倍 + 收盘在日内振幅上方30%\n    - 卖出: 价格跌破突破位3% 或 MA10死叉MA20\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, config: BacktestConfig,\n                 lookback: int = 20,\n                 volume_multiple: float = 2.0,\n                 stop_loss_pct: float = 0.03,\n                 position_pct: float = 0.7):\n        super().__init__(config)\n        self.lookback = lookback\n        self.volume_multiple = volume_multiple\n        self.stop_loss_pct = stop_loss_pct\n        self.position_pct = position_pct\n        self.breakout_price = {}  # 记录突破价格用于止损\n        \n    def on_bar(self, date, bar_data):\n        if self.current_idx < self.lookback + 5:\n            return None\n            \n        hist = self.data.iloc[:self.current_idx + 1]\n        symbol = 'stock'\n        \n        # 20日最高价（不含当天）\n        resistance = hist['high'].iloc[-self.lookback-1:-1].max()\n        \n        # 成交量条件\n        vol_avg5 = hist['volume'].rolling(5).mean().iloc[-2]  # 前一天的5日均量\n        curr_vol = hist['volume'].iloc[-1]\n        volume_ratio = curr_vol / vol_avg5 if vol_avg5 > 0 else 0\n        \n        # 收盘强度（收盘在日内振幅的位置）\n        day_range = bar_data['high'] - bar_data['low']\n        if day_range > 0:\n            close_strength = (bar_data['close'] - bar_data['low']) / day_range\n        else:\n            close_strength = 0.5\n            \n        current_position = self.positions.get(symbol, 0)\n        \n        # 买入信号: 突破阻力 + 放量 + 强势收盘\n        if (bar_data['close'] > resistance and\n            volume_ratio >= self.volume_multiple and\n            close_strength >= 0.7):\n            \n            if current_position == 0:\n                target_value = self.capital * self.position_pct\n                shares = int(target_value / bar_data['close'] / 100) * 100\n                if shares > 0:\n                    self.breakout_price[symbol] = resistance\n                    return {'action': 'BUY', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': shares}\n                    \n        # 卖出信号: 跌破突破位\n        elif current_position > 0:\n            bp = self.breakout_price.get(symbol, 0)\n            if bp > 0 and bar_data['close'] < bp * (1 - self.stop_loss_pct):\n                return {'action': 'SELL', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': current_position}\n                \n        return None\n\n\nclass ShrinkPullbackStrategy(BaseStrategy):\n    \"\"\"\n    缩量回踩策略\n    \n    来源: daily_stock_analysis/strategies/shrink_pullback.yaml\n    \n    逻辑:\n    - 前提: MA5 > MA10 > MA20（多头排列）\n    - 买入: 价格回踩MA5/MA10 + 成交量 < 5日均量70%\n    - 卖出: 价格跌破MA20\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, config: BacktestConfig,\n                 ma_short: int = 5,\n                 ma_mid: int = 10,\n                 ma_long: int = 20,\n                 volume_shrink: float = 0.7,\n                 ma5_touch_pct: float = 0.01,\n                 ma10_touch_pct: float = 0.02,\n                 position_pct: float = 0.8):\n        super().__init__(config)\n        self.ma_short = ma_short\n        self.ma_mid = ma_mid\n        self.ma_long = ma_long\n        self.volume_shrink = volume_shrink\n        self.ma5_touch_pct = ma5_touch_pct\n        self.ma10_touch_pct = ma10_touch_pct\n        self.position_pct = position_pct\n        \n    def on_bar(self, date, bar_data):\n        if self.current_idx < self.ma_long + 5:\n            return None\n            \n        hist = self.data.iloc[:self.current_idx + 1]\n        symbol = 'stock'\n        \n        # 均线\n        ma5 = hist['close'].rolling(self.ma_short).mean().iloc[-1]\n        ma10 = hist['close'].rolling(self.ma_mid).mean().iloc[-1]\n        ma20 = hist['close'].rolling(self.ma_long).mean().iloc[-1]\n        \n        # 多头排列检查\n        is_bullish = ma5 > ma10 > ma20\n        \n        # 成交量缩量检查\n        vol_avg5 = hist['volume'].rolling(5).mean().iloc[-1]\n        curr_vol = hist['volume'].iloc[-1]\n        is_shrink = (curr_vol < vol_avg5 * self.volume_shrink) if vol_avg5 > 0 else False\n        \n        # 回踩MA5\n        dist_ma5 = abs(bar_data['close'] - ma5) / ma5 if ma5 > 0 else 1\n        touch_ma5 = dist_ma5 < self.ma5_touch_pct\n        \n        # 回踩MA10\n        dist_ma10 = abs(bar_data['close'] - ma10) / ma10 if ma10 > 0 else 1\n        touch_ma10 = dist_ma10 < self.ma10_touch_pct\n        \n        current_position = self.positions.get(symbol, 0)\n        \n        # 买入信号\n        if is_bullish and is_shrink and (touch_ma5 or touch_ma10):\n            if current_position == 0:\n                target_value = self.capital * self.position_pct\n                shares = int(target_value / bar_data['close'] / 100) * 100\n                if shares > 0:\n                    return {'action': 'BUY', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': shares}\n                    \n        # 卖出信号: 跌破MA20\n        elif current_position > 0 and bar_data['close'] < ma20:\n            return {'action': 'SELL', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': current_position}\n            \n        return None\n\n\nclass BottomVolumeStrategy(BaseStrategy):\n    \"\"\"\n    底部放量策略\n    \n    来源: daily_stock_analysis/strategies/bottom_volume.yaml\n    \n    逻辑:\n    - 前提: 近60日下跌超过30%\n    - 买入: 成交量突然放大到5日均量3倍 + 收阳线\n    - 卖出: 盈利20%或亏损10%\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, config: BacktestConfig,\n                 decline_period: int = 60,\n                 decline_pct: float = 0.30,\n                 volume_spike: float = 3.0,\n                 take_profit: float = 0.20,\n                 stop_loss: float = 0.10,\n                 position_pct: float = 0.6):\n        super().__init__(config)\n        self.decline_period = decline_period\n        self.decline_pct = decline_pct\n        self.volume_spike = volume_spike\n        self.take_profit = take_profit\n        self.stop_loss = stop_loss\n        self.position_pct = position_pct\n        self.entry_price = {}\n        \n    def on_bar(self, date, bar_data):\n        if self.current_idx < self.decline_period + 5:\n            return None\n            \n        hist = self.data.iloc[:self.current_idx + 1]\n        symbol = 'stock'\n        \n        current_position = self.positions.get(symbol, 0)\n        \n        # 持仓中检查止盈止损\n        if current_position > 0:\n            ep = self.entry_price.get(symbol, bar_data['close'])\n            pnl = (bar_data['close'] - ep) / ep\n            \n            if pnl >= self.take_profit:\n                return {'action': 'SELL', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': current_position}\n            elif pnl <= -self.stop_loss:\n                return {'action': 'SELL', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': current_position}\n            return None\n            \n        # 检查近期跌幅\n        period_high = hist['high'].iloc[-self.decline_period-1:-1].max()\n        decline_ratio = (bar_data['close'] - period_high) / period_high\n        \n        if decline_ratio > -self.decline_pct:\n            return None  # 跌幅不够，不是底部\n            \n        # 放量检查\n        vol_avg5 = hist['volume'].rolling(5).mean().iloc[-2]\n        volume_ratio = bar_data['volume'] / vol_avg5 if vol_avg5 > 0 else 0\n        \n        # 阳线检查\n        is_bullish_candle = bar_data['close'] > bar_data['open']\n        \n        # 买入信号\n        if volume_ratio >= self.volume_spike and is_bullish_candle:\n            target_value = self.capital * self.position_pct\n            shares = int(target_value / bar_data['close'] / 100) * 100\n            if shares > 0:\n                self.entry_price[symbol] = bar_data['close']\n                return {'action': 'BUY', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': shares}\n                \n        return None\n\n\nclass BoxOscillationStrategy(BaseStrategy):\n    \"\"\"\n    箱体震荡策略\n    \n    来源: daily_stock_analysis/strategies/box_oscillation.yaml\n    \n    逻辑:\n    - 识别箱体: 近N日的高低点形成通道\n    - 买入: 价格触及箱体下沿支撑\n    - 卖出: 价格触及箱体上沿阻力 或 跌破箱体下沿\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, config: BacktestConfig,\n                 box_period: int = 20,\n                 support_buffer: float = 0.02,\n                 resistance_buffer: float = 0.02,\n                 breakdown_stop: float = 0.03,\n                 position_pct: float = 0.7):\n        super().__init__(config)\n        self.box_period = box_period\n        self.support_buffer = support_buffer\n        self.resistance_buffer = resistance_buffer\n        self.breakdown_stop = breakdown_stop\n        self.position_pct = position_pct\n        \n    def on_bar(self, date, bar_data):\n        if self.current_idx < self.box_period + 5:\n            return None\n            \n        hist = self.data.iloc[:self.current_idx + 1]\n        symbol = 'stock'\n        \n        # 计算箱体\n        recent = hist.iloc[-self.box_period-1:-1]\n        box_high = recent['high'].max()\n        box_low = recent['low'].min()\n        box_range = box_high - box_low\n        \n        # 箱体有效性: 振幅在5%-30%之间\n        if box_low <= 0:\n            return None\n        box_pct = box_range / box_low\n        if box_pct < 0.05 or box_pct > 0.30:\n            return None\n            \n        current_position = self.positions.get(symbol, 0)\n        \n        # 支撑位和阻力位\n        support = box_low * (1 + self.support_buffer)\n        resistance = box_high * (1 - self.resistance_buffer)\n        breakdown = box_low * (1 - self.breakdown_stop)\n        \n        # 买入信号: 触及支撑\n        if bar_data['close'] <= support and bar_data['close'] > breakdown:\n            if current_position == 0:\n                target_value = self.capital * self.position_pct\n                shares = int(target_value / bar_data['close'] / 100) * 100\n                if shares > 0:\n                    return {'action': 'BUY', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': shares}\n                    \n        # 卖出信号: 触及阻力 或 跌破箱体\n        elif current_position > 0:\n            if bar_data['close'] >= resistance or bar_data['close'] < breakdown:\n                return {'action': 'SELL', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': current_position}\n                \n        return None\n\n\nclass EmotionCycleStrategy(BaseStrategy):\n    \"\"\"\n    情绪周期策略\n    \n    来源: daily_stock_analysis/strategies/emotion_cycle.yaml\n    \n    逻辑:\n    - 用换手率和量比作为情绪代理指标\n    - 买入: 情绪低迷后开始回暖（量比从低位回升）\n    - 卖出: 情绪过热（换手率异常高）\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, config: BacktestConfig,\n                 turnover_high: float = 2.0,   # 换手率高位标准差倍数\n                 turnover_low: float = -1.0,    # 换手率低位标准差倍数\n                 volume_ratio_recovery: float = 1.5,\n                 lookback: int = 20,\n                 position_pct: float = 0.7):\n        super().__init__(config)\n        self.turnover_high = turnover_high\n        self.turnover_low = turnover_low\n        self.volume_ratio_recovery = volume_ratio_recovery\n        self.lookback = lookback\n        self.position_pct = position_pct\n        \n    def on_bar(self, date, bar_data):\n        if self.current_idx < self.lookback + 10:\n            return None\n            \n        hist = self.data.iloc[:self.current_idx + 1]\n        symbol = 'stock'\n        \n        # 用成交量作为情绪代理\n        vol_series = hist['volume'].tail(self.lookback)\n        vol_mean = vol_series.mean()\n        vol_std = vol_series.std()\n        \n        if vol_std == 0:\n            return None\n            \n        # 当前量的z-score\n        curr_vol_z = (hist['volume'].iloc[-1] - vol_mean) / vol_std\n        prev_vol_z = (hist['volume'].iloc[-2] - vol_mean) / vol_std\n        \n        # 量比\n        vol_avg5 = hist['volume'].rolling(5).mean().iloc[-1]\n        volume_ratio = hist['volume'].iloc[-1] / vol_avg5 if vol_avg5 > 0 else 1\n        \n        current_position = self.positions.get(symbol, 0)\n        \n        # 买入信号: 情绪从低迷回暖（量从低位回升）\n        if (prev_vol_z < self.turnover_low and\n            curr_vol_z > self.turnover_low and\n            volume_ratio >= self.volume_ratio_recovery and\n            bar_data['close'] > bar_data['open']):  # 阳线确认\n            \n            if current_position == 0:\n                target_value = self.capital * self.position_pct\n                shares = int(target_value / bar_data['close'] / 100) * 100\n                if shares > 0:\n                    return {'action': 'BUY', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': shares}\n                    \n        # 卖出信号: 情绪过热\n        elif current_position > 0 and curr_vol_z > self.turnover_high:\n            return {'action': 'SELL', 'symbol': symbol, 'shares': current_position}\n            \n        return None\n\n\n# 策略注册表\nSTRATEGY_REGISTRY = {\n    'ma_golden_cross': {\n        'class': MAGoldenCrossStrategy,\n        'name': '均线金叉',\n        'category': 'trend',\n        'source': 'ma_golden_cross.yaml',\n        'default_params': {'ma_short': 5, 'ma_mid': 10, 'ma_long': 20}\n    },\n    'volume_breakout': {\n        'class': VolumeBreakoutStrategy,\n        'name': '放量突破',\n        'category': 'trend',\n        'source': 'volume_breakout.yaml',\n        'default_params': {'lookback': 20, 'volume_multiple': 2.0}\n    },\n    'shrink_pullback': {\n        'class': ShrinkPullbackStrategy,\n        'name': '缩量回踩',\n        'category': 'trend',\n        'source': 'shrink_pullback.yaml',\n        'default_params': {'ma_short': 5, 'ma_mid': 10, 'ma_long': 20}\n    },\n    'bottom_volume': {\n        'class': BottomVolumeStrategy,\n        'name': '底部放量',\n        'category': 'reversal',\n        'source': 'bottom_volume.yaml',\n        'default_params': {'decline_period': 60, 'volume_spike': 3.0}\n    },\n    'box_oscillation': {\n        'class': BoxOscillationStrategy,\n        'name': '箱体震荡',\n        'category': 'range',\n        'source': 'box_oscillation.yaml',\n        'default_params': {'box_period': 20}\n    },\n    'emotion_cycle': {\n        'class': EmotionCycleStrategy,\n        'name': '情绪周期',\n        'category': 'sentiment',\n        'source': 'emotion_cycle.yaml',\n        'default_params': {'lookback': 20}\n    },\n}\n","path":"/Users/ling/quant/strategies/your_strategies/migrated_strategies.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"camel-claude","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":767,"output":6036,"cacheRead":144606,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":151409,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775806186925,"responseId":"bbd77c79-95d7-4893-8e40-3a112b44db87"}}
