{"type":"message","id":"9c1ce20e","parentId":"02152c58","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:46:44.168Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is right. The backtest period is 2024-01 to 2026-04, and the HS300 index went from 3386 to 4636, which is a 36.9% gain. But the best strategy only returned 31.37% - barely matching the index. The user says \"only this much return in more than a year of bull market, the strategy needs more optimization.\"\n\nThis is a valid critique. The strategy is barely matching the index. Let me think about what could be wrong:\n\n1. The RSI strategy is mean-reversion based, which might not work well in a strong trending market\n\n\n2. I should explore trend-following approaches instead - momentum or breakout strategies tend to perform better during bull markets. I could also test on individual stocks rather than just the index, or try a combination approach. The core problem is that my current strategy isn't capturing the upside during a strong trend. Let me build a momentum-based backtester to compare against the mean-reversion approach.","thinkingSignature":"3b3661d12dfd179c18274d6ecd1f19269c8b10a68dce5555118108c200d32350"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n你说得对！沪深300同期涨了**36.9%**（3386→4636），但最好策略只跑出31.37%，连指数都没跑赢。RSI是逆势策略，牛市里会反复被\"洗\"出。让我试试**趋势跟踪策略**：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_071be25faccc4a28bc962687","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport baostock as bs\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport warnings\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\nlg = bs.login()\nrs = bs.query_history_k_data_plus('sh.000300', 'date,open,high,low,close,volume',\n    start_date='2024-01-01', end_date='2026-04-10', frequency='d')\ndata_list = []\nwhile rs.error_code == '0' and rs.next():\n    data_list.append(rs.get_row_data())\ndf = pd.DataFrame(data_list, columns=rs.fields)\ndf['date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['date'])\ndf = df.set_index('date')\nfor col in ['open','high','low','close','volume']:\n    df[col] = pd.to_numeric(df[col], errors='coerce')\ndf = df.dropna()\nbs.logout()\n\nprint(f\"数据: {len(df)} 条\")\nprint(f\"沪深300: {df.iloc[0]['close']:.2f} → {df.iloc[-1]['close']:.2f} ({(df.iloc[-1]['close']/df.iloc[0]['close']-1)*100:.1f}%)\")\nprint(f\"买入持有收益: 36.9%\\n\")\n\ndef backtest(data, strategy_func, name):\n    capital = 100000\n    cash = capital\n    shares = 0\n    trades = []\n    \n    signals = strategy_func(data)\n    \n    for date, row in data.iterrows():\n        if date not in signals.index or pd.isna(signals.loc[date]):\n            continue\n        price = row['close']\n        sig = signals.loc[date]\n        \n        if sig == 1 and cash > price:\n            shares = int(cash / price * 0.95)\n            cash -= shares * price * 1.0003\n            trades.append(('BUY', date.date(), price))\n        elif sig == -1 and shares > 0:\n            cash += shares * price * 0.9997\n            trades.append(('SELL', date.date(), price))\n            shares = 0\n    \n    final = cash + shares * data.iloc[-1]['close']\n    total_ret = (final - capital) / capital\n    annual = (1 + total_ret) ** (252 / len(data)) - 1\n    \n    equity = []\n    tc, ts = capital, 0\n    for date, row in data.iterrows():\n        if date not in signals.index or pd.isna(signals.loc[date]):\n            equity.append(tc + ts * row['close'])\n            continue\n        p = row['close']\n        sig = signals.loc[date]\n        if tc > p and ts == 0 and sig == 1:\n            ts = int(tc / p * 0.95)\n            tc -= ts * p * 1.0003\n        elif ts > 0 and sig == -1:\n            tc += ts * p * 0.9997\n            ts = 0\n        equity.append(tc + ts * p)\n    \n    eq = pd.Series(equity, index=data.index)\n    rets = eq.pct_change().dropna()\n    sharpe = rets.mean() / rets.std() * np.sqrt(252) if rets.std() > 0 else 0\n    peak = eq.cummax()\n    max_dd = ((eq - peak) / peak).min()\n    \n    buys = [t for t in trades if t[0]=='BUY']\n    sells = [t for t in trades if t[0]=='SELL']\n    wins = sum(1 for i,t in enumerate(sells) if i < len(buys) and t[2] > buys[i][2])\n    win = wins / len(sells) if sells else 0\n    \n    return {'name': name, 'total': total_ret, 'annual': annual, 'sharpe': sharpe, 'max_dd': max_dd, 'trades': len(trades), 'win': win}\n\n# === 趋势跟踪策略 ===\n\n# 策略1: 趋势线突破 (短期均线在长期均线上方且均线多头排列)\ndef trend_ma(data, short=5, long=20):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    ma_s = data['close'].rolling(short).mean()\n    ma_l = data['close'].rolling(long).mean()\n    # 趋势: 短 > 长 且 在上涨中\n    uptrend = (ma_s > ma_l) & (ma_s > ma_s.shift(5))\n    sig[uptrend & ~uptrend.shift(1).fillna(False)] = 1  # 刚确认趋势\n    sig[(ma_s < ma_l)] = -1  # 跌破离场\n    return sig\n\n# 策略2: 动量突破\ndef momentum(data, lookback=10, threshold=0.02):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    mom = data['close'].pct_change(lookback)\n    sig[mom > threshold] = 1\n    sig[mom < 0] = -1\n    return sig\n\n# 策略3: 布林带趋势 (价格在中轨上方持有)\ndef boll_trend(data, window=20):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    mid = data['close'].rolling(window).mean()\n    upper = mid + 2 * data['close'].rolling(window).std()\n    # 价格突破布林中轨且均线多头\n    ma5 = data['close'].rolling(5).mean()\n    ma20 = data['close'].rolling(20).mean()\n    buy = (data['close'] > mid) & (ma5 > ma20)\n    sig[buy & ~buy.shift(1).fillna(False)] = 1\n    sig[(data['close'] < mid)] = -1\n    return sig\n\n# 策略4: 高点位突破 (创20日新高持有)\ndef breakout_high(data, window=20):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    high_max = data['high'].rolling(window).max().shift(1)\n    ma20 = data['close'].rolling(20).mean()\n    buy = data['close'] > high_max\n    sig[buy] = 1\n    sig[data['close'] < ma20] = -1\n    return sig\n\n# 策略5: 趋势+RSI组合 (趋势确认时RSI不超买不卖)\ndef trend_rsi(data, ma_short=5, ma_long=20, rsi_period=7, rsi_buy=50, rsi_sell=80):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    ma_s = data['close'].rolling(ma_short).mean()\n    ma_l = data['close'].rolling(ma_long).mean()\n    delta = data['close'].diff()\n    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0).rolling(rsi_period).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(rsi_period).mean()\n    rs = gain / (loss + 1e-10)\n    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\n    \n    # 多头排列时买入\n    buy = (ma_s > ma_l) & (ma_s.shift(1) <= ma_l.shift(1))\n    sig[buy] = 1\n    # RSI超买才卖 (不是死叉就卖)\n    sell = (ma_s < ma_l) | (rsi > rsi_sell)\n    sig[sell] = -1\n    return sig\n\n# 策略6: MACD趋势\ndef macd_trend(data, fast=12, slow=26, signal=9):\n    ema_fast = data['close'].ewm(span=fast, adjust=False).mean()\n    ema_slow = data['close'].ewm(span=slow, adjust=False).mean()\n    dif = ema_fast - ema_slow\n    dea = dif.ewm(span=signal, adjust=False).mean()\n    macd = (dif - dea) * 2\n    \n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    # MACD金叉且在零轴上方\n    golden = (dif > dea) & (dif.shift(1) <= dea.shift(1)) & (dif > 0)\n    death = (dif < dea) & (dif.shift(1) >= dea.shift(1))\n    sig[golden] = 1\n    sig[death] = -1\n    return sig\n\nstrategies = [\n    (\"趋势MA(5/20)\", lambda d: trend_ma(d, 5, 20)),\n    (\"趋势MA(10/30)\", lambda d: trend_ma(d, 10, 30)),\n    (\"动量突破(10)\", lambda d: momentum(d, 10, 0.02)),\n    (\"动量突破(5)\", lambda d: momentum(d, 5, 0.01)),\n    (\"布林趋势\", lambda d: boll_trend(d, 20)),\n    (\"高点突破(20)\", lambda d: breakout_high(d, 20)),\n    (\"趋势RSI\", lambda d: trend_rsi(d)),\n    (\"MACD趋势\", lambda d: macd_trend(d)),\n]\n\nprint(\"=\" * 75)\nprint(\"📈 趋势跟踪策略 vs 买入持有 (36.9%)\")\nprint(\"=\" * 75)\nprint(f\"{'策略':<16} {'总收益':>8} {'年化':>8} {'夏普':>6} {'回撤':>8} {'交易':>5} {'胜率':>6}\")\nprint(\"-\" * 75)\n\nresults = []\nfor name, func in strategies:\n    r = backtest(df, func, name)\n    results.append(r)\n    diff = r['total'] - 0.369\n    mark = \" 🔥\" if diff > 0 else \"\"\n    print(f\"{name:<16} {r['total']:>7.2%} {r['annual']:>7.2%} {r['sharpe']:>6.3f} {r['max_dd']:>7.2%} {r['trades']:>5} {r['win']:>5.1%}{mark}\")\n\nresults.sort(key=lambda x: x['total'], reverse=True)\nprint()\nprint(\"🏆 趋势策略排名:\")\nfor i, r in enumerate(results[:5], 1):\n    print(f\"  {i}. {r['name']}: 总收益={r['total']:.2%} 年化={r['annual']:.2%} 夏普={r['sharpe']:.3f}\")\nEOF","timeout":90}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1057,"output":2635,"cacheRead":68864,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72556,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775814327712,"responseId":"0627f9ba1fcb5cff1cdc7ee47e4fbfcc"}}
