    11.14%   4.98%  0.440 -14.07%    20 40.0%\n趋势MA(5/20)        15.83%   6.99%  0.572 -15.44%    38 31.6%\n动量均线              -7.01%  -3.29% -0.368 -14.60%    42 14.3%\n\n基准: 沪深300买入持有 = 36.9%\n\n🏆 排名:\n  1. 买入持有: 34.98% 年化14.79% 夏普0.875 ❌跑输\n  2. 均线金叉(5/20): 15.83% 年化6.99% 夏普0.572 ❌跑输\n  3. 趋势MA(5/20): 15.83% 年化6.99% 夏普0.572 ❌跑输\n  4. 均线金叉(10/30): 11.14% 年化4.98% 夏普0.440 ❌跑输\n  5. 均线金叉(20/60): 6.16% 年化2.79% 夏普0.303 ❌跑输\n  6. 动量均线: -7.01% 年化-3.29% 夏普-0.368 ❌跑输\n","name":"python3 <<"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775814573080}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a8a3a25","parentId":"99dd2890","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:50:57.301Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The results now make more sense. The buy-and-hold benchmark gives 34.98% (close to 36.9% with dividends/costs adjusted), while all the MA crossover strategies underperform.\n\nThe issue is that in a bull market, trend-following strategies get whipsawed - they buy late and sell early. The RSI mean-reversion strategy at least captures some of the gains (31.37%) but still doesn't beat buy-and-hold.\n\nThe key insight is: in a strong bull market (like 2024-2026 China market), the best strategy is to simply buy and hold. Any active trading strategy will likely underperform due to transaction costs and market noise.\n\nBut wait - the user is right. \n\nIf the index went up 36.9% and the best active strategy only achieves 31.37%, that's disappointing. Let me reconsider the RSI strategy parameters. The original RSI(7, 25, 70) strategy achieved 31.37% with a Sharpe of 1.265, which is solid risk-adjusted performance, but the absolute return still falls short of the buy-and-hold benchmark. I should explore whether optimizing the RSI thresholds or combining it with other indicators could capture more of the upside while maintaining better risk characteristics.\n\nLooking at the buy-and-hold result of 34.98%, that aligns reasonably well with the 36.9% index return when accounting for transaction costs and slippage. The real challenge here is that this market has experienced significant drawdowns of 10-15%, so a buy-and-hold investor would have endured substantial peak-to-trough declines. The RSI strategy's appeal lies in its superior Sharpe ratio (1.265 vs 0.875) and shallower maximum drawdown (-9.55% vs -15.01%), meaning an investor could potentially lever up the RSI approach to improve absolute returns while maintaining better risk-adjusted metrics than the passive alternative.\n\nBut the user's complaint about returns being too low in a bull market is valid. I should explore whether the strategy actually detects and avoids major drawdowns better than holding the index, or if there are ways to improve absolute performance. I could test a hybrid approach that combines trend detection to stay invested during confirmed uptrends while using RSI for tactical adjustments, or try different index proxies that might better capture the market's movements.","thinkingSignature":"2d427ea4b1adea78d3d6a329ed851deb7893744997bdbb71ecf9132bb4e25be1"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n数据正确了。关键发现：**沪深300同期涨36.9%，买入持有34.98%，所有主动策略都跑输指数**。这说明牛市里频繁调仓反而拖累收益。让我分析原因并尝试改进：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_77dd76c3163741ce95e951ad","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport baostock as bs\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport warnings\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\nlg = bs.login()\nrs = bs.query_history_k_data_plus('sh.000300', 'date,open,high,low,close,volume',\n    start_date='2024-01-01', end_date='2026-04-10', frequency='d')\ndata_list = []\nwhile rs.error_code == '0' and rs.next():\n    data_list.append(rs.get_row_data())\ndf = pd.DataFrame(data_list, columns=rs.fields)\ndf['date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['date'])\ndf = df.set_index('date')\nfor col in ['open','high','low','close','volume']:\n    df[col] = pd.to_numeric(df[col], errors='coerce')\ndf = df.dropna()\nbs.logout()\n\nprint(f\"数据: 沪深300 {df.iloc[0]['close']:.2f} → {df.iloc[-1]['close']:.2f} ({(df.iloc[-1]['close']/df.iloc[0]['close']-1)*100:.1f}%)\\n\")\n\n# 分析: 哪些阶段跑输最多?\n# 把沪深300分成多段，看趋势强度\ndf['ma20'] = df['close'].rolling(20).mean()\ndf['ma60'] = df['close'].rolling(60).mean()\ndf['rsi7'] = 100 - (100 / (1 + \n    df['close'].diff().where(df['close'].diff()>0,0).rolling(7).mean() / \n    (-df['close'].diff().where(df['close'].diff()<0,0).rolling(7).mean() + 1e-10)\n))\n\n# 上涨/下跌天数\nup_days = (df['close'] > df['close'].shift(1)).sum()\ndown_days = (df['close'] < df['close'].shift(1)).sum()\nprint(f\"上涨天数: {up_days}, 下跌天数: {down_days}\")\nprint(f\"上涨比例: {up_days/(up_days+down_days):.1%}\")\nprint()\n\n# 改进策略: 只在超卖时买入，但不轻易卖出 (持有到更极端情况)\ndef backtest(data, strategy_func, name):\n    capital = 100000.0\n    cash = capital\n    shares = 0\n    trades = []\n    \n    signals = strategy_func(data)\n    \n    equity_dates = []\n    equity_values = []\n    current_cash = cash\n    current_shares = 0\n    \n    for date, row in data.iterrows():\n        price = row['close']\n        equity_dates.append(date)\n        equity_values.append(current_cash + current_shares * price)\n        \n        if date not in signals.index or pd.isna(signals.loc[date]):\n            continue\n        \n        sig = signals.loc[date]\n        \n        if sig == 1 and current_shares == 0 and current_cash > price:\n            n = int(current_cash / price * 0.95)\n            if n > 0:\n                current_cash -= n * price * 1.0003\n                current_shares = n\n                trades.append(('BUY', date.date(), price))\n        elif sig == -1 and current_shares > 0:\n            current_cash += current_shares * price * 0.9997\n            trades.append(('SELL', date.date(), price))\n            current_shares = 0\n    \n    final_price = data.iloc[-1]['close']\n    final_value = current_cash + current_shares * final_price\n    total_ret = (final_value - capital) / capital\n    annual = (1 + total_ret) ** (252 / len(data)) - 1\n    \n    equity = pd.Series(equity_values, index=equity_dates)\n    returns = equity.pct_change().dropna()\n    sharpe = returns.mean() / returns.std() * np.sqrt(252) if returns.std() > 0 else 0\n    peak = equity.cummax()\n    max_dd = ((equity - peak) / peak).min()\n    \n    buys = [t for t in trades if t[0]=='BUY']\n    sells = [t for t in trades if t[0]=='SELL']\n    wins = sum(1 for i,t in enumerate(sells) if i < len(buys) and t[2] > buys[i][2])\n    win = wins / len(sells) if sells else 0\n    \n    return {'name': name, 'total': total_ret, 'annual': annual, 'sharpe': sharpe, 'max_dd': max_dd, 'trades': len(trades), 'win': win, 'equity': equity}\n\n# 策略A: RSI超卖买入 + 更宽松的卖出 (RSI>85才卖)\ndef rsi_loose(data, rsi_p=7, os=25, ob=85):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    delta = data['close'].diff()\n    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + gain/(loss+1e-10)))\n    sig[rsi < os] = 1\n    sig[rsi > ob] = -1\n    return sig\n\n# 策略B: RSI超卖买入 + 均线死叉才卖\ndef rsi_ma_exit(data, rsi_p=7, os=25, ma_s=5, ma_l=20):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    delta = data['close'].diff()\n    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + gain/(loss+1e-10)))\n    ma_s_ = data['close'].rolling(ma_s).mean()\n    ma_l_ = data['close'].rolling(ma_l).mean()\n    sig[rsi < os] = 1\n    sig[(ma_s_ < ma_l_) & (ma_s_.shift(1) >= ma_l_.shift(1))] = -1\n    return sig\n\n# 策略C: 金字塔买入 (每次RSI<25都加仓)\ndef rsi_pyramid(data, rsi_p=7):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    delta = data['close'].diff()\n    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + gain/(loss+1e-10)))\n    sig[rsi < 25] = 1\n    sig[rsi > 80] = -1\n    return sig\n\n# 策略D: 趋势确认后买入 (RSI<30时 且 均线多头)\ndef rsi_trend(data, rsi_p=7, os=30, ma_s=5, ma_l=20):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    delta = data['close'].diff()\n    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + gain/(loss+1e-10)))\n    ma_s_ = data['close'].rolling(ma_s).mean()\n    ma_l_ = data['close'].rolling(ma_l).mean()\n    # 多头排列时RSI<os买入\n    buy = (rsi < os) & (ma_s_ > ma_l_)\n    sig[buy & ~buy.shift(1).fillna(False)] = 1\n    # 死叉或RSI>85卖出\n    sig[(ma_s_ < ma_l_) & (ma_s_.shift(1) >= ma_l_.shift(1))] = -1\n    sig[rsi > 85] = -1\n    return sig\n\n# 策略E: 持有到RSI>80 (趋势中的回调买入)\ndef rsi_pullback(data, rsi_p=7, os=30, ob=80):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    delta = data['close'].diff()\n    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + gain/(loss+1e-10)))\n    ma5 = data['close'].rolling(5).mean()\n    ma20 = data['close'].rolling(20).mean()\n    # 趋势向上时(ma5>ma20)，RSI<os买入\n    uptrend = ma5 > ma20\n    buy = (rsi < os) & uptrend\n    sig[buy & ~buy.shift(1).fillna(False)] = 1\n    # 跌破均线或RSI>ob卖出\n    sig[(~uptrend) | (rsi > ob)] = -1\n    return sig\n\nstrategies = [\n    (\"RSI(7,25)+宽松卖出85\", lambda d: rsi_loose(d, 7, 25, 85)),\n    (\"RSI(7,25)+均线止盈\", lambda d: rsi_ma_exit(d, 7, 25)),\n    (\"RSI金字塔\", lambda d: rsi_pyramid(d)),\n    (\"RSI+趋势确认\", lambda d: rsi_trend(d)),\n    (\"RSI回调买入\", lambda d: rsi_pullback(d)),\n    (\"RSI(7,20,80)\", lambda d: rsi_loose(d, 7, 20, 80)),\n    (\"RSI(7,30,85)\", lambda d: rsi_loose(d, 7, 30, 85)),\n]\n\nprint(\"=\" * 75)\nprint(\"📈 改进策略 vs 买入持有 (34.98%)\")\nprint(\"=\" * 75)\nprint(f\"{'策略':<22} {'总收益':>8} {'年化':>8} {'夏普':>6} {'回撤':>8} {'交易':>5} {'胜率':>6}\")\nprint(\"-\" * 75)\n\nresults = []\nfor name, func in strategies:\n    r = backtest(df, func, name)\n    results.append(r)\n    diff = r['total'] - 0.3498\n    mark = \" 🔥\" if diff > 0 else \"\"\n    print(f\"{name:<22} {r['total']:>7.2%} {r['annual']:>7.2%} {r['sharpe']:>6.3f} {r['max_dd']:>7.2%} {r['trades']:>5} {r['win']:>5.1%}{mark}\")\n\nresults.sort(key=lambda x: x['total'], reverse=True)\nprint()\nprint(\"🏆 排名:\")\nbenchmark = 0.3498\nfor i, r in enumerate(results, 1):\n    diff = r['total'] - benchmark\n    beat = f\"{diff:+.2%}\" if diff != 0 else \"=\"\n    print(f\"  {i}. {r['name']}: {r['total']:.2%} (vs基准{beat}) 夏普{r['sharpe']:.3f} 回撤{r['max_dd']:.2%}\")\nEOF","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":630,"output":3133,"cacheRead":75008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78771,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775814573094,"responseId":"0627faaf72622c731f182cdfd06ce2d2"}}
