{"type":"message","id":"83496d3b","parentId":"71bdb0aa","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:31:02.253Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The best strategy found so far is still only 21.86% annual return, far below the 50% target. The issue is that in this market period (2024-2026), even the best strategies are capped around 20-22% annual because the market itself only returned 36.9% total (~15% annual).\n\nTo achieve 50% annual, the strategy would need to be extremely aggressive or use leverage. But there's a fundamental limit - you can't consistently get 50% annual from a market that only goes up 15% per year without using leverage or taking on much more risk.\n\nLet me try:\n1. Higher position sizing (using margin/financing)\n2. More frequent trading with smaller stops\n\n\n3. Multiple positions and sector rotation to capture more market opportunities\n\nBut fundamentally, achieving 50% annual in a market that only appreciates 15% annually would require either extreme leverage with correspondingly extreme risk, or a strategy that perfectly times every local minimum and maximum - which is unrealistic. I should be upfront about this constraint rather than chasing an impossible target.\n","thinkingSignature":"aab613ee0bcc3696831339c6064169f903d5f4a119db8b3e41d044bd397fc6d0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n年化50%在沪深300同期年化仅~15%的基础上，几乎不可能不靠杠杆。让我尝试更激进方案（带止损+全仓+杠杆）：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cdd7a27051024cd595ae636a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport baostock as bs\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport warnings\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\nlg = bs.login()\nrs = bs.query_history_k_data_plus('sh.000300', 'date,open,high,low,close,volume',\n    start_date='2024-01-01', end_date='2026-04-10', frequency='d')\ndata_list = []\nwhile rs.error_code == '0' and rs.next():\n    data_list.append(rs.get_row_data())\ndf = pd.DataFrame(data_list, columns=rs.fields)\ndf['date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['date'])\ndf = df.set_index('date')\nfor col in ['open','high','low','close','volume']:\n    df[col] = pd.to_numeric(df[col], errors='coerce')\ndf = df.dropna()\nbs.logout()\n\nbenchmark = (df.iloc[-1]['close'] / df.iloc[0]['close'] - 1) * 100\nprint(f\"沪深300: {benchmark:.1f}%, 年化约15%\\n\")\n\ndef backtest_leveraged(data, signals, position_pct=1.0, trailing_stop=None):\n    \"\"\"支持杠杆和追踪止损\"\"\"\n    capital = 100000.0\n    cash = capital\n    shares = 0\n    trades = []\n    peak_price = 0\n    \n    equity_dates = []\n    equity_values = []\n    c = cash\n    s = 0\n    pp = 0\n    \n    for date, row in data.iterrows():\n        price = row['close']\n        equity_dates.append(date)\n        equity_values.append(c + s * price)\n        \n        if date not in signals.index or pd.isna(signals.loc[date]):\n            continue\n        \n        sig = signals.loc[date]\n        \n        # 追踪止损\n        if trailing_stop and s > 0:\n            if price > pp:\n                pp = price\n            if price < pp * (1 - trailing_stop):\n                c += s * price * 0.9997\n                trades.append(('SELL', date.date(), price, 'TS'))\n                s = 0\n                pp = 0\n        \n        if sig == 1 and s == 0:\n            n = int(c * position_pct / price)\n            if n > 0:\n                cost = n * price * 1.0003\n                c -= cost\n                s = n\n                pp = price\n                trades.append(('BUY', date.date(), price))\n        elif sig == -1 and s > 0:\n            c += s * price * 0.9997\n            trades.append(('SELL', date.date(), price))\n            s = 0\n            pp = 0\n    \n    fv = c + s * data.iloc[-1]['close']\n    tr = (fv - capital) / capital\n    \n    equity = pd.Series(equity_values, index=equity_dates)\n    rets = equity.pct_change().dropna()\n    sharpe = rets.mean() / rets.std() * np.sqrt(252) if rets.std() > 0 else 0\n    peak = equity.cummax()\n    max_dd = ((equity - peak) / peak).min()\n    \n    buys = [t for t in trades if t[0]=='BUY']\n    sells = [t for t in trades if t[0]=='SELL']\n    wins = sum(1 for i,t in enumerate(sells) if i < len(buys) and t[2] > buys[i][2])\n    win = wins / len(sells) if sells else 0\n    \n    return {\n        'total': tr * 100,\n        'annual': ((1+tr)**(252/len(data))-1) * 100,\n        'sharpe': sharpe,\n        'max_dd': max_dd * 100,\n        'trades': len(trades),\n        'win': win * 100\n    }\n\n# RSI + 均线止盈 (最佳基础策略)\ndef rsi_ma(data, rp=7, os=25, ms=8, ml=25):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    delta = data['close'].diff()\n    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0).rolling(rp).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(rp).mean()\n    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + gain/(loss+1e-10)))\n    ma_s = data['close'].rolling(ms).mean()\n    ma_l = data['close'].rolling(ml).mean()\n    sig[rsi < os] = 1\n    sig[(ma_s < ma_l) & (ma_s.shift(1) >= ma_l.shift(1))] = -1\n    return sig\n\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\nprint(\"💰 杠杆策略测试 (目标年化50%+)\")\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\nprint(f\"{'策略':<30} {'总收益':>8} {'年化':>8} {'夏普':>6} {'回撤':>8} {'交易':>5}\")\nprint(\"-\" * 70)\n\nall_results = []\n\n# 测试不同杠杆/仓位\nfor pos in [0.95, 1.0, 1.05, 1.1, 1.15, 1.2]:\n    sig = rsi_ma(df, 7, 25, 8, 25)\n    r = backtest_leveraged(df, sig, position_pct=pos)\n    all_results.append((f\"RSI(7,25)MA(8/25) 仓位{pos*100:.0f}%\", r))\n\n# 测试追踪止损\nfor ts in [0.05, 0.08, 0.10, 0.12, 0.15]:\n    sig = rsi_ma(df, 7, 25, 8, 25)\n    r = backtest_leveraged(df, sig, position_pct=1.0, trailing_stop=ts)\n    all_results.append((f\"RSI(7,25)MA(8/25) TS{ts*100:.0f}%\", r))\n\n# 激进RSI + 杠杆\nfor rp in [3, 4, 5]:\n    for os in [15, 20, 25]:\n        sig = rsi_ma(df, rp, os, 8, 25)\n        r = backtest_leveraged(df, sig, position_pct=1.2)\n        all_results.append((f\"RSI({rp},{os})MA(8/25) 120%仓位\", r))\n\n# RSI追踪止损激进\ndef rsi_ts(data, rp=5, os=20, ts_pct=0.08):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    delta = data['close'].diff()\n    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0).rolling(rp).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(rp).mean()\n    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + gain/(loss+1e-10)))\n    sig[rsi < os] = 1\n    sig[rsi > 80] = -1\n    return sig\n\nfor rp in [3, 5, 7]:\n    for os in [15, 20, 25]:\n        for ts in [0.05, 0.08, 0.10]:\n            sig = rsi_ts(df, rp, os, ts)\n            r = backtest_leveraged(df, sig, position_pct=1.2)\n            all_results.append((f\"RSI({rp},{os})TS{ts*100:.0f}% 120%\", r))\n\nall_results.sort(key=lambda x: x[1]['annual'], reverse=True)\n\nfor name, r in all_results[:15]:\n    print(f\"{name:<30} {r['total']:>7.2f}% {r['annual']:>7.2f}% {r['sharpe']:>6.3f} {r['max_dd']:>7.2f}% {r['trades']:>5}\")\n\nprint()\nbest_name, best_r = all_results[0]\nprint(f\"🏆 最佳: {best_name}\")\nprint(f\"   总收益: {best_r['total']:.2f}% | 年化: {best_r['annual']:.2f}%\")\nprint(f\"   夏普: {best_r['sharpe']:.3f} | 回撤: {best_r['max_dd']:.2f}%\")\n\n# 诚实评估\nprint()\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\nprint(\"⚠️ 诚实评估\")\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\nprint(f\"沪深300年化仅~15%，策略最高年化{best_r['annual']:.1f}%\")\nprint(\"年化50%需要远超市场的超额收益（α），现实中:\")\nprint(\"  1. 需要高频/短线交易（手续费会吃掉大部分利润）\")\nprint(\"  2. 需要融资杠杆（放大收益也放大亏损）\")\nprint(\"  3. 过去表现不代表未来\")\nprint(f\"\\n当前最优: {best_name} 年化{best_r['annual']:.1f}%\")\nEOF","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3254,"output":2313,"cacheRead":88768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94335,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775820623704,"responseId":"06281250fe537943c2e11ff20674f662"}}
