{"type":"message","id":"271a0058","parentId":"50ac7e64","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:31:54.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The results show that even with leverage (120% position) and various optimizations, the best annual return is around 28.17%. That's still far from the 50% target. Let me think about what's realistic...\n\nThe沪深300 (CSI 300) itself only returned about 15% annualized over this period. A strategy that beats it by a significant margin is already good. To expect 50% annualized means generating 3.3x the market return, which is extremely ambitious.\n\nLet me try a few more things:\n1. More aggressive stop-loss (cut losses quickly)\n2. Shorter-term trading (more frequent signals)\n\n\n3. Partial position management (add to winners)\n4. Try with individual stocks instead of index\n\nBut honestly, I should be transparent - 50% annualized from a CSI 300-based strategy is extremely aggressive and unrealistic. Let me try a few more approaches and then be honest with the user.","thinkingSignature":"954ddba37f037f6e2d32a7448e95a156f3281e74e3a2615087380d7396a7c88b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**诚实评估：沪深300年化仅~15%，当前最优策略年化28.2%，距离50%目标差距很大。**\n\n让我再试几种极端方案：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_606f8c9ec0534ec98b5135a5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport baostock as bs\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport warnings\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\nlg = bs.login()\nrs = bs.query_history_k_data_plus('sh.000300', 'date,open,high,low,close,volume',\n    start_date='2024-01-01', end_date='2026-04-10', frequency='d')\ndata_list = []\nwhile rs.error_code == '0' and rs.next():\n    data_list.append(rs.get_row_data())\ndf = pd.DataFrame(data_list, columns=rs.fields)\ndf['date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['date'])\ndf = df.set_index('date')\nfor col in ['open','high','low','close','volume']:\n    df[col] = pd.to_numeric(df[col], errors='coerce')\ndf = df.dropna()\nbs.logout()\n\ndef backtest_full(data, signals, pos=1.0):\n    capital = 100000.0\n    c, s = capital, 0\n    trades = []\n    pp = 0\n    \n    equity_vals = []\n    for date, row in data.iterrows():\n        price = row['close']\n        equity_vals.append(c + s * price)\n        \n        if date not in signals.index or pd.isna(signals.loc[date]):\n            continue\n        sig = signals.loc[date]\n        \n        if sig == 1 and s == 0:\n            n = int(c * pos / price)\n            if n > 0:\n                c -= n * price * 1.0003\n                s = n\n                pp = price\n                trades.append(('B', date.date(), price))\n        elif sig == -1 and s > 0:\n            c += s * price * 0.9997\n            trades.append(('S', date.date(), price))\n            s = 0\n    \n    fv = c + s * data.iloc[-1]['close']\n    tr = (fv - capital) / capital\n    \n    eq = pd.Series(equity_vals, index=data.index)\n    rets = eq.pct_change().dropna()\n    sharpe = rets.mean() / rets.std() * np.sqrt(252) if rets.std() > 0 else 0\n    peak = eq.cummax()\n    max_dd = ((eq - peak) / peak).min()\n    \n    buys = [t for t in trades if t[0]=='B']\n    sells = [t for t in trades if t[0]=='S']\n    wins = sum(1 for i,t in enumerate(sells) if i < len(buys) and t[2] > buys[i][2])\n    win = wins / len(sells) if sells else 0\n    \n    return {'total': tr*100, 'annual': ((1+tr)**(252/len(data))-1)*100, 'sharpe': sharpe, 'max_dd': max_dd*100, 'trades': len(trades), 'win': win*100}\n\n# 极短线策略: 日内/隔日\ndef ultra_short(data, rsi_p=3, os=20, ob=80):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    delta = data['close'].diff()\n    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + gain/(loss+1e-10)))\n    sig[rsi < os] = 1\n    sig[rsi > ob] = -1\n    return sig\n\n# 金字塔加仓\ndef pyramid(data, rsi_p=7, os=25):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    delta = data['close'].diff()\n    gain = delta.where(delta > 0, 0).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(rsi_p).mean()\n    rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + gain/(loss+1e-10)))\n    sig[rsi < os] = 1\n    sig[rsi > 75] = -1\n    return sig\n\n# MACD短线\ndef macd_short(data, f=5, s=13, sig=6):\n    ema_f = data['close'].ewm(span=f, adjust=False).mean()\n    ema_s_ = data['close'].ewm(span=s, adjust=False).mean()\n    dif = ema_f - ema_s_\n    dea = dif.ewm(span=sig, adjust=False).mean()\n    macd = (dif - dea) * 2\n    \n    sig_out = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    golden = (dif > dea) & (dif.shift(1) <= dea.shift(1)) & (dif > 0)\n    death = (dif < dea) & (dif.shift(1) >= dea.shift(1))\n    sig_out[golden] = 1\n    sig_out[death] = -1\n    return sig_out\n\n# 双RSI确认\ndef dual_rsi(data, rp1=3, rp2=7, os=25):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    d = data['close'].diff()\n    \n    g1 = d.where(d>0,0).rolling(rp1).mean()\n    l1 = (-d.where(d<0,0)).rolling(rp1).mean()\n    rsi1 = 100 - (100/(1+g1/(l1+1e-10)))\n    \n    g2 = d.where(d>0,0).rolling(rp2).mean()\n    l2 = (-d.where(d<0,0)).rolling(rp2).mean()\n    rsi2 = 100 - (100/(1+g2/(l2+1e-10)))\n    \n    # 两个RSI都超卖才买\n    buy = (rsi1 < os) & (rsi2 < os)\n    sig[buy & ~buy.shift(1).fillna(False)] = 1\n    sig[rsi1 > 75] = -1\n    return sig\n\nprint(\"=\" * 65)\nprint(\"🔥 极短线策略测试\")\nprint(\"=\" * 65)\nprint(f\"{'策略':<25} {'总收益':>8} {'年化':>8} {'夏普':>6} {'回撤':>8} {'交易':>5}\")\nprint(\"-\" * 65)\n\nall_results = []\n\n# 极短线\nfor rp in [2, 3, 4, 5]:\n    for os in [15, 20, 25, 30]:\n        for ob in [70, 75, 80, 85]:\n            sig = ultra_short(df, rp, os, ob)\n            r = backtest_full(df, sig, pos=1.0)\n            all_results.append((f\"极短线RSI({rp},{os},{ob})\", r))\n\n# MACD短线\nsig = macd_short(df, 5, 13, 6)\nr = backtest_full(df, sig, pos=1.0)\nall_results.append((\"MACD短线(5,13,6)\", r))\n\nsig = macd_short(df, 3, 10, 5)\nr = backtest_full(df, sig, pos=1.0)\nall_results.append((\"MACD短线(3,10,5)\", r))\n\n# 金字塔\nfor rp in [5, 7]:\n    for os in [20, 25, 30]:\n        sig = pyramid(df, rp, os)\n        r = backtest_full(df, sig, pos=1.2)\n        all_results.append((f\"金字塔RSI({rp},{os})120%\", r))\n\n# 双RSI\nfor rp1 in [3, 5]:\n    for rp2 in [7, 10]:\n        for os in [20, 25, 30]:\n            sig = dual_rsi(df, rp1, rp2, os)\n            r = backtest_full(df, sig, pos=1.0)\n            all_results.append((f\"双RSI({rp1},{rp2},{os})\", r))\n\n# 结合均线\ndef rsi_ma_short(data, rp=3, os=20, ms=3, ml=10):\n    sig = pd.Series(0, index=data.index)\n    d = data['close'].diff()\n    g = d.where(d>0,0).rolling(rp).mean()\n    l = (-d.where(d<0,0)).rolling(rp).mean()\n    rsi = 100 - (100/(1+g/(l+1e-10)))\n    ma_s = data['close'].rolling(ms).mean()\n    ma_l = data['close'].rolling(ml).mean()\n    sig[rsi < os] = 1\n    sig[(ma_s < ma_l) & (ma_s.shift(1) >= ma_l.shift(1))] = -1\n    return sig\n\nfor rp in [3, 5, 7]:\n    for os in [20, 25, 30]:\n        for ms in [3, 5]:\n            for ml in [10, 15, 20]:\n                if ms >= ml: continue\n                sig = rsi_ma_short(df, rp, os, ms, ml)\n                r = backtest_full(df, sig, pos=1.0)\n                all_results.append((f\"RSI({rp},{os})MA({ms}/{ml})\", r))\n\nall_results.sort(key=lambda x: x[1]['annual'], reverse=True)\n\nfor name, r in all_results[:15]:\n    print(f\"{name:<25} {r['total']:>7.2f}% {r['annual']:>7.2f}% {r['sharpe']:>6.3f} {r['max_dd']:>7.2f}% {r['trades']:>5}\")\n\nprint()\nbest_name, best_r = all_results[0]\nprint(f\"🏆 最佳: {best_name}\")\nprint(f\"   年化: {best_r['annual']:.2f}% (回撤: {best_r['max_dd']:.2f}%)\")\n\nprint()\nprint(\"=\" * 65)\nprint(\"📌 结论\")\nprint(\"=\" * 65)\nprint(f\"沪深300年化~15%，当前最佳年化{best_r['annual']:.1f}%\")\nprint(\"年化50%需要:\")\nprint(\"  1. 融资杠杆 (如2x则理论年化56%，但风险加倍)\")\nprint(\"  2. 换到波动更大的个股/期货\")\nprint(\"  3. 高频炒单 (但手续费会大幅侵蚀)\")\nprint()\nprint(\"现实建议: 接受~25-28%年化已是优秀水平\")\nEOF","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3035,"output":2638,"cacheRead":91968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97641,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775820670439,"responseId":"0628127ef73853d4ac81c30f67de9ece"}}
