{"type":"message","id":"a2623846","parentId":"35d5d549","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:32:09.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The results show that the best strategy found was RSI(7,25)MA(5/20) with 19.77% annual return, but the previous best with 120% position and trailing stop gave 28.17%. The 28.17% was the highest we found.\n\nLet me compile the best results and present them to the user clearly, with an honest assessment that年化50% on the沪深300 is extremely ambitious.\n\nThe honest answer is:\n- 沪深300 itself only grew ~15% annualized during this period\n- The best strategy we found was 28.17% annualized with 120% position (leverage)\n\n\n- Achieving 50% annualized would require either leveraging 2x on that strategy, switching to higher-volatility instruments like futures or individual stocks, or adopting a much more aggressive trading approach\n","thinkingSignature":"1ce6896d0669cb61ef6d98b577229a9521d7ac43df284b615915cc50ca46f971"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**最终结论**：\n\n| 策略 | 年化 | 夏普 | 回撤 | vs沪深300 |\n|------|------|------|------|-----------|\n| RSI(7,25)MA(8/25) **120%仓位** | **28.17%** | 1.297 | -16.68% | +13.2% |\n| RSI(7,25)MA(8/25) **追踪止损5%** | **27.45%** | 1.498 | -11.00% | +12.5% |\n| RSI(7,25)MA(8/25) 115%仓位 | 27.01% | 1.299 | -16.02% | +12.0% |\n| 沪深300 买入持有 | ~15% | 0.875 | -15% | 基准 |\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ 诚实说：**\n\n沪深300 2024-2026年化只有**~15%**，策略能做到**28%**已是极限。\n\n**年化50%需要**：\n1. **2x杠杆** → 把28%变成56%，但回撤也会从-17%变成-34%\n2. **换到期货/个股** → 波动更大，机会更大但风险也大\n3. **高频炒单** → 手续费会吃掉大部分利润\n\n**现实建议**：接受 **25-30%年化** 是优秀水平。28%年化已经比巴菲特还高。要继续挑战50%，需要加杠杆或者换高波动品种。要试吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3250,"output":507,"cacheRead":94976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98733,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775820719552,"responseId":"062812afbbe7e22b21da6a1b90ee431e"}}
