%  0.361   -30.8%   114   +2.5% 🔥\nRSI(14,30)MA(8/60)           87.1%     4.1%  0.307   -45.4%    73   +2.4% 🔥\nRSI(5,20)MA(10/60)           85.8%     4.0%  0.300   -41.0%    83   +2.4% 🔥\nRSI(5,25)MA(10/20)           83.2%     3.9%  0.302   -41.7%   209   +2.3% 🔥\nRSI(7,20)MA(8/60)            77.2%     3.7%  0.287   -38.9%    79   +2.0% 🔥\nRSI(10,30)MA(10/60)          75.8%     3.7%  0.282   -44.3%    79   +2.0% 🔥\nRSI(5,20)MA(5/60)            75.6%     3.7%  0.283   -37.9%   105   +2.0% 🔥\n\n基准沪深300: 总31.2% | 年化1.7%\n\n🏆 最佳: RSI(14,20)MA(10/60)\n   总收益: 182.4% | 年化: 6.8%\n   夏普: 0.510 | 最大回撤: -27.0%\n   交易: 44次 | 胜率: 63.6%\n   vs基准: +5.2%\n\n📊 分阶段表现:\n   2015牛市: 沪深300 +141.2%\n   2015熊市: 沪深300 -44.9%\n   近3年: 沪深300 +36.9%\n","name":"python3 <<"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775820843463}}
{"type":"message","id":"25d535bb","parentId":"5f1f414b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:34:13.587Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is very interesting. Over the long term (2010-2026, about 16 years), the CSI 300 only returned 31.2% total (1.7% annual). This is because 2010-2014 was a bear market, and 2018 was also bad. But the strategy still beat the market.\n\nThe best strategy over the long term is RSI(14,20)MA(10/60) with:\n- Total return: 182.4%\n- Annual: 6.8%\n- Sharpe: 0.510\n- Max drawdown: -27.0%\n- vs benchmark: +5.2%\n\n\nBut even the best strategy only achieves 6.8% annually, which falls well short of the 50% target. The core issue is that 2010-2024 was a challenging period for Chinese stocks—the CSI 300 essentially went sideways for years. If I want to hit 50% annualized returns, I'd need to shift to individual stocks with higher volatility or explore entirely different approaches.","thinkingSignature":"60b495a762b5a151ce895d173163ac63c0323d6e62c64913ac6b4c961ef47bb0"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n结果出来了！但这个数据揭示了一个重要事实：\n\n**📊 长期回测 (2010-2026，16年)**\n\n| 指标 | 沪深300 | 最佳策略 |\n|------|---------|----------|\n| 总收益 | 31.2% | **182.4%** |\n| 年化 | **1.7%** | **6.8%** |\n| 夏普 | - | 0.510 |\n| 回撤 | - | -27.0% |\n| vs基准 | - | **+5.2%** |\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ 残酷的事实：**\n\n沪深300在2010-2024年这14年间**几乎没涨**（熊市长熊）！2010年初到2024年初还在原地。\n\n策略年化6.8%已经**大幅跑赢基准**（+5.2%/年），但距离50%年化目标**差距巨大**。\n\n**16年穿越牛熊，年化才6.8%**。年化50%在这段数据上**根本不可能实现**，除非：\n1. 加杠杆\n2. 换高波动品种（个股/期货）\n3. 接受极高回撤风险\n\n**结论**：在这段历史数据上，策略已经做到极致（跑赢指数5%+）。**不加杠杆不可能年化50%**。这不只是策略问题，是市场本身回报率有限。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1234,"output":511,"cacheRead":101120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102865,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775820843470,"responseId":"0628132c88a0c4d157dbf698d9bc50f2"}}
