{"type":"message","id":"d038ad4d","parentId":"a9ff2c9d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T11:41:49.256Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The results show that:\n\n1. 中证1000 (CSI 1000 - small cap index) from 2015-2026:\n   - Total return: 32.2%\n   - Annual return: only 2.5%\n   - The index barely moved! From 6049 to 7998 over 11 years is very poor performance.\n\n2. Best strategy on 中证1000:\n   - RSI(5,30)MA(8/60): 53.5% total, 4.0% annual\n   - Sharpe: 0.284 (very low)\n   - Max drawdown: -64.4% (huge!)\n   - Only beat the benchmark by +1.5% annual\n\nThis is actually worse than the 沪深300 strategies! The small cap index 2015-2026 was a terrible investment. 2015 was the peak of the small cap bubble, then it crashed badly and never recovered.\n\nThe user wants 年化50% but the data shows:\n- 中证1000 annual return: 2.5%\n- Best strategy annual: 4.0%\n- Gap to 50%: 46 percentage points\n\nThis is simply impossible without leverage. The small cap index itself was a terrible investment from 2015-2026 because:\n1. 2015 bubble burst\n2. Then many years of small cap underperformance vs large caps\n\nLet me be honest with the user about this.","thinkingSignature":"5c5080fa643b8fa74c426c77fd26e59ee6352814da0aab059337c2ab97c070d6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n中证1000结果出来了，但更残酷：\n\n**📊 中证1000 (小市值指数) 2015-2026**\n\n| 指标 | 中证1000 | 最佳策略 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| 总收益 | 32.2% | **53.5%** |\n| 年化 | **2.5%** | **4.0%** |\n| 夏普 | - | 0.284 |\n| 最大回撤 | - | **-64.4%** |\n| vs基准 | - | +1.5% |\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ 更残酷的事实：**\n\n中证1000在2015年牛市顶峰后**11年几乎没涨**（2015年初是大泡沫顶点）。最佳策略年化才**4%**，最大回撤**-64%**！\n\n回测期间选错了——2015年初是历史最高点，之后小市值连续多年跑输大盘。\n\n**结论**：\n- 小市值策略回撤巨大（-64%），风险极高\n- 年化4%依然离50%目标差距巨大\n- **2015年至今，小市值指数本身表现极差**\n\n你想：\n1. 换到**2010年之前**的数据（2008熊市底部开始？小市值那时候还没上市）\n2. 尝试**期货/商品**（波动更大）\n3. 还是接受现实，**年化50%在A股不可能不加杠杆**？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3161,"output":607,"cacheRead":102848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106616,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775821294174,"responseId":"062814eeddd877cabbf18376694f377f"}}
