{"type":"message","id":"4d566c5a","parentId":"d5109263","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:40:08.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"oMLX is a local LLM inference server for Apple Silicon (M1/M2/M3/M4) using the MLX framework. It provides a native macOS menu bar app for managing the server, monitoring status, and downloading models. It's optimized for Apple Silicon and has features like continuous batching and SSD caching.","thinkingSignature":"adb0184457a0dfd08c7ff1c9a600669b51b8ed26272fabbb29d85d4e74b70c50"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**oMLX** 是一个运行在 macOS 菜单栏的 **本地 LLM 推理服务器**，专门为 Apple Silicon (M1/M2/M3/M4) 优化。\n\n**主要功能**：\n- 🖥️ 菜单栏应用，无需终端即可管理\n- 🚀 使用 Apple MLX 框架高性能推理\n- 💾 SSD KV 缓存，节省显存\n- 📥 可下载模型\n- ⚙️ 支持 Claude Code 等工具\n\n**简单说**：在你 Mac 上跑本地大模型的服务器，菜单栏控制界面。\n\n你之前有安装过吗？现在运行成功了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1537,"output":194,"cacheRead":134976,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136707,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775828400870,"responseId":"062830b1f3798d7455bd2daa77680e3d"}}
