{"type":"message","id":"8d536a25","parentId":"41909135","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:40:22.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they can see oMLX in the menu bar but can't open it by double-clicking. Let me check what's happening - maybe it's just a menu bar app (no window by default) and needs to be clicked once to open a menu, not double-clicked.","thinkingSignature":"a796b77c589dac47d8fbb58a0b79089880caf9006206b054b51a5394277d6c74"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\noMLX 是**菜单栏应用**，不需要双击。直接**单击**菜单栏的图标即可打开。\n\n如果菜单栏看不到图标，可能需要：\n1. 点击右上角菜单栏最右边的小箭头展开隐藏图标\n2. 或者检查 `系统设置 → 菜单栏 → oMLX` 是否启用\n\n你能在菜单栏看到 oMLX 图标吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":477,"output":139,"cacheRead":136448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137064,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775828415839,"responseId":"062830c095bbc1214695c967d1fc72b6"}}
