{"type":"message","id":"c8e5c6de","parentId":"79fff78b","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:42:00.097Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says they can't open oMLX even though the process is running. The process is running (oMLX appears in the process list) but there's no GUI window appearing.\n\nLet me think about what could be wrong:\n1. The app might be running but its menu bar item isn't appearing (perhaps due to macOS menu bar settings)\n2. The app might be crashing immediately after launching (no GUI)\n3. There might be a display/GUI issue\n\nSince the process is running but no window appears, this is likely a GUI/display issue. Let me check if the app has any visible windows or if it's running headless.\n\nLet me also check if there's a display issue or if the app is launching in background mode.","thinkingSignature":"c9ff1bc4a0e0990a96b6791117dbc09eaa529496932d4d40bab6f003f258e74f"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n进程在运行但没有界面。可能是菜单栏图标被隐藏了。\n\n试试：\n1. 点击右上角菜单栏的 **\"<<\"** 箭头展开隐藏图标\n2. 或者 **系统设置 → 菜单栏 → oMLX** 设置为\"始终显示\"\n\n如果还是看不到，尝试这个命令强制显示：\n\n```\nkillall oMLX && sleep 1 && open -a oMLX && sleep 3 && osascript -e 'tell application \"oMLX\" to activate'\n```\n\n能看到菜单栏图标吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":607,"output":263,"cacheRead":138240,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139110,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775828512154,"responseId":"0628312021323d8275b4f795f3c874d2"}}
