{"type":"message","id":"96ecb50d","parentId":"bac3f29d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:44:36.571Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The app runs but immediately exits with SIGKILL. This could be a macOS security restriction - the app is being killed because it doesn't have proper entitlements or the system is blocking it.\n\nLet me check if there's a notarization issue or if the app is being killed by System Integrity Protection or something else. Also let me try running it with `open` command instead.","thinkingSignature":"a2a32fa298b91c1a208292730bf27f2fd36c3db54c9a94af483d7489a8f022df"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f1a04149977e463ba0a1ff2f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查是否被系统杀死\necho \"=== 系统完整性检查 ===\"\ncsrutil status 2>/dev/null\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 检查App Sandbox ===\"\ncodesign -dvv \"/Applications/oMLX.app\" 2>&1 | grep -i \"entitle\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 尝试用 open 命令 ===\"\nopen -a oMLX --args --debug 2>&1 &\nsleep 3\necho \"---\"\npgrep -l oMLX","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":190,"output":210,"cacheRead":139392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":139792,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775828669163,"responseId":"062831bd192a234402a5788541e19977"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e94bf891","parentId":"96ecb50d","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:44:39.821Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f1a04149977e463ba0a1ff2f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== 系统完整性检查 ===\nSystem Integrity Protection status: enabled.\n\n=== 检查App Sandbox ===\n\n=== 尝试用 open 命令 ===\n---\n9030 oMLX"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3202,"aggregated":"=== 系统完整性检查 ===\nSystem Integrity Protection status: enabled.\n\n=== 检查App Sandbox ===\n\n=== 尝试用 open 命令 ===\n---\n9030 oMLX","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775828679816}}
{"type":"message","id":"f7308f45","parentId":"e94bf891","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:44:47.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The app is running but SIP is enabled and the app seems to have no sandbox entitlements showing. The app is launching but the menu bar click isn't working. This could be a PyObjC/NSStatusItem issue where the click event isn't being captured properly.\n\nLet me check if there's a specific issue with the app's event handling or if there's a way to debug this further. Maybe I should check the GitHub issues for this specific problem.","thinkingSignature":"5b33170ef617725e97d598e4d39438f2718ec2c9a4c14629041f42c864e27755"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5e086dec76a7497bb1700f8b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 查看GitHub issues提到的相关问题\necho \"检查是否有权限问题...\"\nsqlite3 ~/Library/Application\\ Support/oMLX/*.db \".tables\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"无数据库\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"检查App Support目录...\"\nls -la ~/Library/Application\\ Support/ 2>/dev/null | grep -i omlx\n\necho \"\"\necho \"尝试强制显示...\"\nkillall oMLX 2>/dev/null\nsleep 1\n\n# 检查系统事件日志\nlog show --predicate 'eventMessage contains \"oMLX\"' --last 1m 2>/dev/null | tail -10","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":240,"output":254,"cacheRead":139520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140014,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775828679824,"responseId":"062831c86efdbab9fa4fe41c64620ba7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1eceffa7","parentId":"f7308f45","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:44:48.964Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5e086dec76a7497bb1700f8b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"检查是否有权限问题...\n无数据库\n\n检查App Support目录...\ndrwxr-xr-x@  4 ling  staff    128 Mar 14 11:52 oMLX\n\n尝试强制显示...\nzsh:3: no matches found: /Users/ling/Library/Application Support/oMLX/*.db"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1113,"aggregated":"检查是否有权限问题...\n无数据库\n\n检查App Support目录...\ndrwxr-xr-x@  4 ling  staff    128 Mar 14 11:52 oMLX\n\n尝试强制显示...\nzsh:3: no matches found: /Users/ling/Library/Application Support/oMLX/*.db","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775828688947}}
{"type":"message","id":"690e1a6d","parentId":"1eceffa7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:44:56.787Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The app is running but the menu bar click isn't responding. Let me check the preferences and try to understand why the popover isn't showing. Maybe there's a display issue or the popover window is being created off-screen.","thinkingSignature":"49ce5e5dc8617c96e06998cfba8127315816295ddfb54c0ad626ca1ac73ff128"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_75dd241c618644cbbbc251c4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查oMLX的偏好设置\ncat ~/Library/Application\\ Support/oMLX/*.json 2>/dev/null || ls -la ~/Library/Application\\ Support/oMLX/\n\necho \"---\"\n# 检查是否有关闭按钮的窗口\nosascript -e 'tell application \"System Events\" to tell process \"oMLX\" to get windows' 2>/dev/null\n\necho \"---\"\n# 尝试用 Accessibility 查看 UI 元素\nosascript -e 'tell application \"System Events\" to tell process \"oMLX\" to get entire contents of front window' 2>/dev/null | head -20","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":292,"output":210,"cacheRead":139712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140214,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775828688967,"responseId":"062831d1c1fd4c34bb8f816dd9e71c51"}}
