{"type":"message","id":"2d398200","parentId":"0ce5b43a","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:45:24.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The UI automation can't see the oMLX menu items. This suggests the menu bar UI might not be properly registered with the accessibility system. Let me try a different approach - maybe we need to grant accessibility permissions or there's a GUI initialization issue.\n\nLet me check if there are any accessibility permissions issues and also try to see if we can launch the app with different arguments to see its window.","thinkingSignature":"4b85516c319397fce59a88c5a96147ae5ac2624c87a829abcf5143d814148c15"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9bdf5c921ff8469882009162","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查Accessibility权限\necho \"=== Accessibility 权限 ===\"\nosascript -e 'tell application \"System Events\" to return processes' 2>&1 | head -3\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 检查oMLX的NSPopOver状态 ===\"\n# 尝试用defaults查看配置\ndefaults read com.omlx.app 2>/dev/null || echo \"无com.omlx.app偏好设置\"\n\necho \"\"\n# 检查是否有窗口但被遮挡\nosascript << 'EOF'\ntell application \"System Events\"\n    tell process \"oMLX\"\n        set visibleWindows to every window whose visible is true\n        return count of visibleWindows\n    end tell\nend tell\nEOF","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":209,"output":255,"cacheRead":140224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140688,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775828716033,"responseId":"062831ec2f15d7b01acfe847007a40a9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"230563c5","parentId":"2d398200","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:45:26.665Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9bdf5c921ff8469882009162","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Accessibility 权限 ===\napplication process loginwindow, application process universalaccessd, application process CoreServicesUIAgent, application process AXVisualSupportAgent, application process ControlCenter, application process Terminal, application process System Settings, application process Feishu, application process WindowManager, application process talagentd, application process chronod, application process Microsoft Edge, application process Shadowrocket, application process Safari, application process SystemUIServer, application process Dock, application process QuickLookUIService, application process Finder, application process WallpaperAgent, application process SCIM_Extension, application process PAH_Extension, application process baiduNetdiskSync, application process NotificationCenter, application process CoreLocationAgent, application process AccessibilityUIServer, application process Spotlight, application process WiFiAgent, application process UIKitSystem, application process BackgroundTaskManagementAgent, application process AppSSOAgent, application process com.apple.dock.extra, application process com.apple.WebKit.GPU, application process LaunchHelper, application process UniversalControl, application process GeneralSettings, application process ARDAgent, application process SSMenuAgent, application process com.apple.WebKit.Networking, application process studentd, application process SoftwareUpdateNotificationManager, application process com.apple.Safari.SandboxBroker, application process GamePolicyAgent, application process com.apple.WebKit.GPU, application process Lark Helper, application process AppleIDSettings, application process com.apple.WebKit.WebContent, application process VPN, application process FollowUpSettingsExtension, application process HeadphoneSettingsExtension, application process FamilySettings, application process ClassroomSettings, application process familycircled, application process TextInputMenuAgent, application process AirPlayUIAgent, application process Raycast, application process HapiGo, application process UURemote, application process UserNotificationCenter, application process TextInputSwitcher, application process UURemoteServer, application process logioptionsplus_agent, application process com.apple.SafariPlatformSupport.Helper, application process com.apple.WebKit.Networking, application process com.apple.WebKit.GPU, application process com.apple.WebKit.WebContent, application process molty, application process Tuxera NTFS, application process com.apple.appkit.xpc.openAndSavePanelService, application process SogouServices, application process com.apple.WebKit.Networking, application process QuickLookUIService, application process com.apple.WebKit.GPU, application process com.apple.WebKit.WebContent, application process Lark Helper, application process logioptionsplus_logivoice, application process Ollama, application process node, application process com.apple.SafariPlatformSupport.Helper, application process LogiPluginService, application process AuthenticationServicesAgent, application process com.apple.SafariPlatformSupport.Helper, application process DockHelper, application process System Events, application process FolderActionsDispatcher, application process SoftwareUpdateSettingsExtension, application process osascript\n\n=== 检查oMLX的NSPopOver状态 ===\n无com.omlx.app偏好设置\n\n87:121: execution error: “System Events”遇到一个错误：不能获得“process \"oMLX\"”。 (-1728)\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":1747,"aggregated":"=== Accessibility 权限 ===\napplication process loginwindow, application process universalaccessd, application process CoreServicesUIAgent, application process AXVisualSupportAgent, application process ControlCenter, application process Terminal, application process System Settings, application process Feishu, application process WindowManager, application process talagentd, application process chronod, application process Microsoft Edge, application process Shadowrocket, application process Safari, application process SystemUIServer, application process Dock, application process QuickLookUIService, application process Finder, application process WallpaperAgent, application process SCIM_Extension, application process PAH_Extension, application process baiduNetdiskSync, application process NotificationCenter, application process CoreLocationAgent, application process AccessibilityUIServer, application process Spotlight, application process WiFiAgent, application process UIKitSystem, application process BackgroundTaskManagementAgent, application process AppSSOAgent, application process com.apple.dock.extra, application process com.apple.WebKit.GPU, application process LaunchHelper, application process UniversalControl, application process GeneralSettings, application process ARDAgent, application process SSMenuAgent, application process com.apple.WebKit.Networking, application process studentd, application process SoftwareUpdateNotificationManager, application process com.apple.Safari.SandboxBroker, application process GamePolicyAgent, application process com.apple.WebKit.GPU, application process Lark Helper, application process AppleIDSettings, application process com.apple.WebKit.WebContent, application process VPN, application process FollowUpSettingsExtension, application process HeadphoneSettingsExtension, application process FamilySettings, application process ClassroomSettings, application process familycircled, application process TextInputMenuAgent, application process AirPlayUIAgent, application process Raycast, application process HapiGo, application process UURemote, application process UserNotificationCenter, application process TextInputSwitcher, application process UURemoteServer, application process logioptionsplus_agent, application process com.apple.SafariPlatformSupport.Helper, application process com.apple.WebKit.Networking, application process com.apple.WebKit.GPU, application process com.apple.WebKit.WebContent, application process molty, application process Tuxera NTFS, application process com.apple.appkit.xpc.openAndSavePanelService, application process SogouServices, application process com.apple.WebKit.Networking, application process QuickLookUIService, application process com.apple.WebKit.GPU, application process com.apple.WebKit.WebContent, application process Lark Helper, application process logioptionsplus_logivoice, application process Ollama, application process node, application process com.apple.SafariPlatformSupport.Helper, application process LogiPluginService, application process AuthenticationServicesAgent, application process com.apple.SafariPlatformSupport.Helper, application process DockHelper, application process System Events, application process FolderActionsDispatcher, application process SoftwareUpdateSettingsExtension, application process osascript\n\n=== 检查oMLX的NSPopOver状态 ===\n无com.omlx.app偏好设置\n\n87:121: execution error: “System Events”遇到一个错误：不能获得“process \"oMLX\"”。 (-1728)\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775828726656}}
{"type":"message","id":"ddfeeac8","parentId":"230563c5","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:45:35.650Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The error \"-1728\" means \"can't get process oMLX\" - the process exists but System Events can't interact with it. This could mean:\n1. Accessibility permissions not granted for System Events to control oMLX\n2. The app doesn't expose standard UI elements that System Events can see\n\nThe menu bar icon is visible but clicking does nothing. This could be:\n1. A bug in the app where the popover menu doesn't respond\n2. Missing Accessibility permissions for the app itself\n\nLet me check if there's an issue with the app itself - maybe we need to reset it or reinstall. Also let me check if there's a way to open the main window directly.","thinkingSignature":"9e1474bada4a01796d914c57023fc8cc01ca0ac39805bdc056a8d5b6a7828eb4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n问题找到了：**System Events 无法与 oMLX 交互**（错误 -1728）。\n\n这说明 oMLX 的菜单栏弹出窗口没有响应点击。\n\n尝试修复：\n\n1. **重置 oMLX 配置**\n2. **重新安装**\n\n```\n# 停止oMLX\nkillall oMLX 2>/dev/null\n\n# 删除配置（不删除模型）\nrm -rf ~/Library/Application\\ Support/oMLX/config.json\n\n# 重启\nopen -a oMLX\n```\n\n能试试吗？如果还是不行，可能需要重新安装 oMLX。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":834,"output":260,"cacheRead":140416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775828726668,"responseId":"062831f756a58d88857840eb3ecfa91a"}}
