"node_id\":\"RA_kwDORPkI2s4XScbm\",\"name\":\"oMLX-0.3.5.dev1-macos15-sequoia.dmg\",\"label\":\"\",\"uploader\":{\"login\":\"jundot\",\"id\":64250138,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjY0MjUwMTM4\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64250138?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/jundot\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"content_type\":\"application/x-apple-diskimage\",\"state\":\"uploaded\",\"size\":779517626,\"digest\":\"sha256:54db1e151b66eccbdd9b32aa89eaf141e9ef23a4ef13430a87588e0443a3ecae\",\"download_count\":2170,\"created_at\":\"2026-04-07T10:13:37Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-07T10:14:46Z\",\"browser_download_url\":\"https://github.com/jundot/omlx/releases/download/v0.3.5.dev1/oMLX-0.3.5.dev1-macos15-sequoia.dmg\"},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/jundot/omlx/releases/assets/390711013\",\"id\":390711013,\"node_id\":\"RA_kwDORPkI2s4XScbl\",\"name\":\"oMLX-0.3.5.dev1-macos26-tahoe.dmg\",\"label\":\"\",\"uploader\":{\"login\":\"jundot\",\"id\":64250138,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjY0MjUwMTM4\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/64250138?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/jundot\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/jundot/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"content_type\":\"application/x-apple-diskimage\",\"state\":\"uploaded\",\"size\":792354103,\"digest\":\"sha256:e2e7665271c5b58c2641e819eba09577f239323569b813ac8cebf79746383a4b\",\"download_count\":7950,\"created_at\":\"2026-04-07T10:13:37Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-07T10:14:49Z\",\"browser_download_url\":\"https://github.com/jundot/omlx/releases/download/v0.3.5.dev1/oMLX-0.3.5.dev1-macos26-tahoe.dmg\"}],\"tarball_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/jundot/omlx/tarball/v0.3.5.dev1\",\"zipball_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/jundot/omlx/zipball/v0.3.5.dev1\",\"body\":\"> Dev release with Gemma 4 native tool calling, UI improvements, and several bug fixes. This is a dev build and may contain bugs. If you run into any issues, please open an issue.\\n\\n## Highlights\\n\\n### Gemma 4 native tool calling\\n\\nBumped mlx-lm to [dcbf6e3](https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx-lm/commit/dcbf6e3) and mlx-vlm to [23e1dff](https://github.com/Blaizzy/mlx-vlm/commit/23e1dff). mlx-lm now ships a native Gemma 4 tool call parser (`<|tool_call>` / `<tool_call|>`) and multi-token think/tool token support. omlx's existing `parse_tool_calls()` picks up the new parser automatically — no server-side special-casing needed.\\n\\nRemoved the Gemma 4 multi-image vision monkey patch since mlx-vlm handles different-sized images natively now. The batched decode patch stays for now (mlx-vlm still uses `cache.state` based KV sharing).\\n\\n### Auto theme mode\\n\\nSystem appearance sync with auto/light/dark theme picker in the admin UI. by @Stv-X (#621, #624)\\n\\n### New Features\\n\\n- Reproducible generation via `seed` parameter (#640)\\n- 6-bit and 8-bit TurboQuant options (#594)\\n- Skip admin auth when `skip_api_key_verification` is enabled on localhost (#587)\\n- Unify `max_num_seqs` and `completion_batch_size` into `max_concurrent_requests`\\n\\n### Bug Fixes\\n\\n- Fix TurboQuant SSD cache reconstruction crash (#577)\\n- Fix oQ: skip quantizing modules without `to_quantized()` (#625)\\n- Fix oQ: unwrap tuple layer outputs in sensitivity measurement (#627)\\n- Fix dark mode heading visibility and mobile UX in chat page (#586)\\n- Fix navbar theme picker width clipping\\n- Fix Homebrew formula sha256 for v0.3.4 (#589)\\n- Fix trigger formula update on release publish instead of tag push\\n- Bundle spacy `en_core_web_sm` for Kokoro TTS in DMG build (#590)\\n- Add missing TTS/STT/STS deps to audio extra (#590)\\n\\n### Dependencies\\n\\n- Bump mlx-lm to dcbf6e3 (Gemma 4 tool call parser, multi-token think/tool)\\n- Bump mlx-vlm to 23e1dff (Gemma 4 multi-image fix, nested tool parser)\\n- Add `regex` dependency\\n\\n### New Contributors\\n\\n- @Stv-X — Auto theme mode and settings UI (#621, #624)\\n\\n**Full changelog**: https://github.com/jundot/omlx/compare/v0.3.4...v0.3.5.dev1\",\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/jundot/omlx/releases/306021576/reactions\",\"total_count\":36,\"+1\":19,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":8,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":9,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"mentions_count\":1}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2824,"aggregated":"jundot/omlx/omlx\nmlx\n{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/jundot/omlx/releases/306021576\",\"assets_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/jundot/omlx/releases/306021576/assets\",